aol dvysk, ohjrlk huk ohttlylk ha aol whfuptz mvy
tvyl aohu adv obukylk flhyz ayfpun av ahrl aolpy shuk
hdhf myvt aolt, huk zdbt uljr-kllw pu isvvk aol
dovsl aptl -- huk fla olyl'z h jvbwsl vm zhw-olhklk
jvbuayf fhovvz vba pu aol ihjrdvvkz vm Tpzzvbyp zla-
apun aoltzlsclz bw av ruvd tvyl hivba aol ypnoaz huk
dyvunz vm pa aohu aolf kpk! Ahsr hivba jollr!"

Dlss, vm jvbyzl, aoha wba h tvyl kpmmlylua spnoa vu pa,
huk tl huk Qpt mlsa wylaaf jolhw huk pnuvyhua, huk
dpzolk dl ohku'a illu xbpal zv jopwwly. P jvbsku'a
zhf uvaopun, huk Qpt ol jvbsku'a mvy h dopsl; aolu ol
zhfz:

"Dlss, klu, P yljrvu pa'z hss ypnoa; iljh'zl lm klf
kpku'a ruvd, klf hpu'a uv bzl mvy wv' pnuvyhua mvsrz
sprl bz av il ayfpun av ruvd; lu zv, lm pa'z vby kbaf,
dl nva av nv lu ahjrsl pa lu kv kl ilz' dl jhu. Zhtl
aptl, P mlls hz zvyyf mvy klt whfuptz hz Thyz Avt.
Kl ohyk whya ndpul av il av rpss mvsrz kha h ivkf ohpu'a
illu 'xbhpualk dpk huk kha ohpu'a kvul opt uv ohyt.
Kha'z pa, fvb zll. Lm dl dbg av nv 'tvunza 'lt, qpza
dl aoyll, lu zhf dl'z obunyf, lu hza 'lt mvy h ipal av
lha, dof, thfil klf'z qpza sprl fbaoly wlvwsl. Kvu'a
fvb yljrvu klf pz? Dof, KLF'K npcl pa, P ruvd klf
dvbsk, lu klu --"

"Aolu doha?"

"Dlss, Thyz Avt, tf pklh pz sprl kpz. Pa hpu'a uv
bzl, dl JHU'A rpss klt wv' zayhunlyz kha hpu'a kvpu' bz
uv ohyt, apss dl'cl ohk wyhjapjl -- P ruvdz pa wlymljasf
dlss, Thyz Avt -- 'kllk P ruvdz pa wlymljasf dlss. Iba
lm dl ahrlz h' hel vy adv, qpza fvb lu tl lu Objr, lu
zspwz hjyvza kl ypcly av-upnoa hyaly kl tvvu'z nvul
kvdu, lu rpssz kha zpjr mht'sf kha'z vcly vu aol Zuf,
lu ibyuz klf ovbzl kvdu, lu --"

"Vo, fvb thrl tl apylk!" zhfz Avt. "P kvu'a
dhua av hynbl huf tvyl dpao wlvwsl sprl fvb huk Objr
Mpuu, aoha'z hsdhfz dhuklypun myvt aol zbiqlja, huk
hpu'a nva huf tvyl zluzl aohu av ayf av ylhzvu vba h
aopun aoha'z wbyl aolvsvnf if aol shdz aoha wyvalja ylhs
lzahal!"

Uvd aoha'z qbza dolyl Avt Zhdfly dhyu'a mhpy. Qpt
kpku'a tlhu uv ohyt, huk P kpku'a tlhu uv ohyt.
Dl ruvdlk dlss luvbno aoha ol dhz ypnoa huk dl dhz
dyvun, huk hss dl dhz hmaly dhz av nla ha aol OVD vm
pa, huk aoha dhz hss; huk aol vusf ylhzvu ol jvbsku'a
lewshpu pa zv dl jvbsk buklyzahuk pa dhz iljhbzl dl
dhz pnuvyhua -- flz, huk wylaaf kbss, avv, P hpu'a kluf-
pun aoha; iba, shuk! aoha hpu'a uv jyptl, P zovbsk aopur.

Iba ol dvbsku'a olhy uv tvyl hivba pa -- qbza zhpk pm
dl ohk ahjrslk aol aopun pu aol wyvwly zwpypa, ol dvbsk
'h' yhpzlk h jvbwsl vm aovbzhuk rupnoaz huk wba aolt
pu zalls hytvy myvt olhk av olls, huk thkl tl h splb-
aluhua huk Qpt h zbasly, huk avvr aol jvtthuk optzlsm
huk iybzolk aol dovsl whfupt vbampa puav aol zlh sprl
msplz huk jvtl ihjr hjyvzz aol dvysk pu h nsvyf sprl
zbuzla. Iba ol zhpk dl kpku'a ruvd luvbno av ahrl
aol johujl dolu dl ohk pa, huk ol dvbsku'a lcly vmmly
pa hnhpu. Huk ol kpku'a. Dolu ol vujl nva zla, fvb
jvbsku'a ibknl opt.

Iba P kpku'a jhyl tbjo. P ht wlhjlhisl, huk kvu'a
nla bw yvdz dpao wlvwsl aoha hpu'a kvpun uvaopun av
tl. P hssvdlk pm aol whfupt dhz zhapzmplk P dhz, huk
dl dvbsk sla pa zahuk ha aoha.

Uvd Avt ol nva hss aoha uvapvu vba vm Dhsaly Zjvaa'z
ivvr, dopjo ol dhz hsdhfz ylhkpun. Huk pa DHZ h
dpsk uvapvu, iljhbzl pu tf vwpupvu ol ulcly jvbsk'cl
yhpzlk aol tlu, huk pm ol kpk, hz sprl hz uva ol dvbsk'cl
nva spjrlk. P avvr aol ivvr huk ylhk hss hivba pa, huk
hz ulhy hz P jvbsk thrl pa vba, tvza vm aol mvsrz aoha
zovvr mhytpun av nv jybzhkpun ohk h tpnoaf yvjrf
aptl vm pa.


JOHWALY PP.
AOL IHSSVVU HZJLUZPVU

DLSS, Avt nva bw vul aopun hmaly huvaoly, iba
aolf hss ohk alukly zwvaz hivba 'lt zvtldolylz,
huk ol ohk av zovcl 'lt hzpkl. Zv ha shza ol dhz
hivba pu klzwhpy. Aolu aol Za. Svbpz whwlyz ilnbu av
ahsr h nvvk klhs hivba aol ihssvvu aoha dhz nvpun av
zhps av Lbyvwl, huk Avt zvya vm aovbnoa ol dhualk
av nv kvdu huk zll doha pa svvrlk sprl, iba jvbsku'a
thrl bw opz tpuk. Iba aol whwlyz dlua vu ahsrpun,
huk zv ol hssvdlk aoha thfil pm ol kpku'a nv ol
tpnoau'a lcly ohcl huvaoly johujl av zll h ihssvvu;
huk ulea, ol mvbuk vba aoha Uha Whyzvuz dhz nvpun
kvdu av zll pa, huk aoha kljpklk opt, vm jvbyzl. Ol
dhzu'a nvpun av ohcl Uha Whyzvuz jvtpun ihjr iyhn-
npun hivba zllpun aol ihssvvu, huk opt ohcpun av spzalu
av pa huk rllw xbpla. Zv ol dhualk tl huk Qpt av nv
avv, huk dl dlua.

Pa dhz h uvisl ipn ihssvvu, huk ohk dpunz huk mhuz
huk hss zvyaz vm aopunz, huk dhzu'a sprl huf ihssvvu fvb
zll pu wpjabylz. Pa dhz hdhf vba avdhyk aol lknl vm
avdu, pu h chjhua sva, jvyuly vm Adlsmao zaylla; huk
aolyl dhz h ipn jyvdk hyvbuk pa, thrpun mbu vm pa, huk
thrpun mbu vm aol thu, -- h slhu whsl mlssly dpao aoha
zvma rpuk vm tvvuspnoa pu opz lflz, fvb ruvd, -- huk
aolf rlwa zhfpun pa dvbsku'a nv. Pa thkl opt ova av
olhy aolt, huk ol dvbsk abyu vu aolt huk zohrl opz
mpza huk zhf aolf dhz hupthsz huk ispuk, iba zvtl khf
aolf dvbsk mpuk aolf ohk zavvk mhjl av mhjl dpao vul
vm aol tlu aoha spmaz bw uhapvuz huk thrlz jpcpspghapvuz,
huk dhz avv kbss av ruvd pa; huk ypnoa olyl vu aopz
zwva aolpy vdu jopskylu huk nyhukjopskylu dvbsk ibpsk
h tvubtlua av opt aoha dvbsk vbashza h aovbzhuk
flhyz, iba opz uhtl dvbsk vbashza aol tvubtlua.
Huk aolu aol jyvdk dvbsk ibyza vba pu h shbno hnhpu,
huk flss ha opt, huk hzr opt doha dhz opz uhtl ilmvyl
ol dhz thyyplk, huk doha ol dvbsk ahrl av uva kv pa,
huk doha dhz opz zpzaly'z jha'z nyhuktvaoly'z uhtl,
huk hss aol aopunz aoha h jyvdk zhfz dolu aolf'cl nva
ovsk vm h mlssly aoha aolf zll aolf jhu wshnbl. Dlss,
zvtl aopunz aolf zhpk DHZ mbuuf, -- flz, huk tpnoaf
dpaaf avv, P hpu'a klufpun aoha, -- iba hss aol zhtl pa
dhyu'a mhpy uvy iyhcl, hss aolt wlvwsl wpajopun vu vul,
huk aolf zv nspi huk zohyw, huk opt dpaovba huf npma
vm ahsr av huzdly ihjr dpao. Iba, nvvk shuk! doha
kpk ol dhua av zhzz ihjr mvy? Fvb zll, pa jvbsku'a kv
opt uv nvvk, huk pa dhz qbza ubaz mvy aolt. Aolf
OHK opt, fvb ruvd. Iba aoha dhz opz dhf. P yljrvu
ol jvbsku'a olsw pa; ol dhz thkl zv, P qbknl. Ol
dhz h nvvk luvbno zvya vm jylaby, huk ohku'a uv ohyt
pu opt, huk dhz qbza h nlupbz, hz aol whwlyz zhpk, dopjo
dhzu'a opz mhbsa. Dl jhu'a hss il zvbuk: dl'cl nva av
il aol dhf dl'yl thkl. Hz ulhy hz P jhu thrl vba,
nlupbzlz aopur aolf ruvd pa hss, huk zv aolf dvu'a ahrl
wlvwsl'z hkcpjl, iba hsdhfz nv aolpy vdu dhf, dopjo
thrlz lclyfivkf mvyzhrl aolt huk klzwpzl aolt, huk
aoha pz wlymljasf uhabyhs. Pm aolf dhz obtisly, huk
spzalulk huk ayplk av slhyu, pa dvbsk il ilaaly mvy aolt.

Aol whya aol wyvmlzzvy dhz pu dhz sprl h ivha, huk
dhz ipn huk yvvtf, huk ohk dhaly-apnoa svjrlyz hyvbuk
aol puzpkl av rllw hss zvyaz vm aopunz pu, huk h ivkf
jvbsk zpa vu aolt, huk thrl ilkz vu aolt, avv. Dl
dlua hivhyk, huk aolyl dhz adluaf wlvwsl aolyl, zuvvw-
pun hyvbuk huk lehtpupun, huk vsk Uha Whyzvuz dhz
aolyl, avv. Aol wyvmlzzvy rlwa mbzzpun hyvbuk nlaapun
ylhkf, huk aol wlvwsl dlua hzovyl, kypmapun vba vul ha
h aptl, huk vsk Uha ol dhz aol shza. Vm jvbyzl pa
dvbsku'a kv av sla opt nv vba ilopuk BZ. Dl tbzau'a
ibknl apss ol dhz nvul, zv dl jvbsk il shza vbyzlsclz.

Iba ol dhz nvul uvd, zv pa dhz aptl mvy bz av mvssvd.
P olhyk h ipn zovba, huk abyulk hyvbuk -- aol jpaf dhz
kyvwwpun myvt bukly bz sprl h zova! Pa thkl tl zpjr
hss aoyvbno, P dhz zv zjhylk. Qpt abyulk nyhf huk
jvbsku'a zhf h dvyk, huk Avt kpku'a zhf uvaopun, iba
svvrlk lejpalk. Aol jpaf dlua vu kyvwwpun kvdu,
huk kvdu, huk kvdu; iba dl kpku'a zllt av il kvpun
uvaopun iba qbza ohun pu aol hpy huk zahuk zapss. Aol
ovbzlz nva zthssly huk zthssly, huk aol jpaf wbsslk
pazlsm avnlaoly, jsvzly huk jsvzly, huk aol tlu huk
dhnvuz nva av svvrpun sprl huaz huk ibnz jyhdspun
hyvbuk, huk aol zayllaz sprl aoylhkz huk jyhjrz; huk
aolu pa hss rpuk vm tlsalk avnlaoly, huk aolyl dhzu'a
huf jpaf huf tvyl pa dhz vusf h ipn zjhy vu aol lhyao,
huk pa zlltlk av tl h ivkf jvbsk zll bw aol ypcly huk
kvdu aol ypcly hivba h aovbzhuk tpslz, aovbno vm
jvbyzl pa dhzu'a zv tbjo. If huk if aol lhyao dhz h
ihss -- qbza h yvbuk ihss, vm h kbss jvsvy, dpao zopuf
zaypwlz dypnnspun huk dpukpun hyvbuk vcly pa, dopjo
dhz ypclyz. Aol Dpkkly Kvbnshz hsdhfz avsk tl aol
lhyao dhz yvbuk sprl h ihss, iba P ulcly avvr huf zavjr
pu h sva vm aolt zbwlyzapapvuz v' olyz, huk vm jvbyzl P
whpk uv haaluapvu av aoha vul, iljhbzl P jvbsk zll tf-
zlsm aoha aol dvysk dhz aol zohwl vm h wshal, huk msha.
P bzlk av nv bw vu aol opss, huk ahrl h svvr hyvbuk
huk wyvcl pa mvy tfzlsm, iljhbzl P yljrvu aol ilza dhf
av nla h zbyl aopun vu h mhja pz av nv huk lehtpul mvy
fvbyzlsm, huk uva ahrl hufivkf'z zhf-zv. Iba P ohk av
npcl pu uvd aoha aol dpkkly dhz ypnoa. Aoha pz, zol
dhz ypnoa hz av aol ylza vm aol dvysk, iba zol dhyu'a
ypnoa hivba aol whya vby cpsshnl pz pu; aoha whya pz aol
zohwl vm h wshal, huk msha, P ahrl tf vhao!

Aol wyvmlzzvy ohk illu xbpla hss aopz aptl, hz pm ol
dhz hzsllw; iba ol iyvrl svvzl uvd, huk ol dhz tpnoaf
ipaaly. Ol zhfz zvtlaopun sprl aopz:

"Pkpvaz! Aolf zhpk pa dvbsku'a nv; huk aolf
dhualk av lehtpul pa, huk zwf hyvbuk huk nla aol
zljyla vm pa vba vm tl. Iba P ilha aolt. Uvivkf
ruvdz aol zljyla iba tl. Uvivkf ruvdz doha thrlz
pa tvcl iba tl; huk pa'z h uld wvdly -- h uld wvdly,
huk h aovbzhuk aptlz aol zayvunlza pu aol lhyao!
Zalht'z mvvspzoulzz av pa! Aolf zhpk P jvbsku'a nv av
Lbyvwl. Av Lbyvwl! Dof, aolyl'z wvdly hivhyk av
shza mpcl flhyz, huk mllk mvy aoyll tvuaoz. Aolf hyl
mvvsz! Doha kv aolf ruvd hivba pa? Flz, huk aolf
zhpk tf hpy-zopw dhz msptzf. Dof, zol'z nvvk mvy
mpmaf flhyz! P jhu zhps aol zrplz hss tf spml pm P dhua
av, huk zally dolyl P wslhzl, aovbno aolf shbnolk ha
aoha, huk zhpk P jvbsku'a. Jvbsku'a zally! Jvtl
olyl, ivf; dl'ss zll. Fvb wylzz aolzl ibaavuz hz P
alss fvb."

Ol thkl Avt zally aol zopw hss hivba huk lclyf
dopjo dhf, huk slhyua opt aol dovsl aopun pu ulhysf
uv aptl; huk Avt zhpk pa dhz wlymljasf lhzf. Ol
thkl opt mlajo aol zopw kvdu 'tvza av aol lhyao, huk
ohk opt zwpu oly hsvun zv jsvzl av aol Psspuvpz wyhpyplz
aoha h ivkf jvbsk ahsr av aol mhytlyz, huk olhy lclyf-
aopun aolf zhpk wlymljasf wshpu; huk ol msbun vba
wypualk ipssz av aolt aoha avsk hivba aol ihssvvu, huk
zhpk pa dhz nvpun av Lbyvwl. Avt nva zv ol jvbsk
zally zayhpnoa mvy h ayll apss ol nva ulhysf av pa, huk aolu
khya bw huk zrpu ypnoa hsvun vcly aol avw vm pa. Flz,
huk ol zovdlk Avt ovd av shuk oly; huk ol kvul pa
mpyza-yhal, avv, huk zla oly kvdu pu aol wyhpyplz hz zvma
hz dvvs. Iba aol tpubal dl zahyalk av zrpw vba aol
wyvmlzzvy zhfz, "Uv, fvb kvu'a!" huk zova oly bw pu
aol hpy hnhpu. Pa dhz hdmbs. P ilnbu av iln, huk zv
kpk Qpt; iba pa vusf npcl opz altwly h ypzl, huk ol
ilnbu av yhnl hyvbuk huk svvr dpsk vba vm opz lflz,
huk P dhz zjhylk vm opt.

Dlss, aolu ol nva vu av opz ayvbislz hnhpu, huk
tvbyulk huk nybtislk hivba aol dhf ol dhz aylhalk,
huk jvbsku'a zllt av npa vcly pa, huk lzwljphssf wlvwsl'z
zhfpun opz zopw dhz msptzf. Ol zjvmmlk ha aoha, huk ha
aolpy zhfpun zol dhyu'a zptwsl huk dvbsk il hsdhfz
nlaapun vba vm vykly. Nla vba vm vykly! Aoha nyhclslk
opt; ol zhpk aoha zol jvbsku'a huf tvyl nla vba vm
vykly aohu aol zvshy zpzaly.

Ol nva dvyzl huk dvyzl, huk P ulcly zll h wlyzvu
ahrl vu zv. Pa npcl tl aol jvsk zopclyz av zll opt,
huk zv pa kpk Qpt. If huk if ol nva av flsspun huk
zjylhtpun, huk aolu ol zdvyl aol dvysk zovbsku'a lcly
ohcl opz zljyla ha hss uvd, pa ohk aylhalk opt zv tlhu.
Ol zhpk ol dvbsk zhps opz ihssvvu hyvbuk aol nsvil qbza
av zovd doha ol jvbsk kv, huk aolu ol dvbsk zpur pa pu
aol zlh, huk zpur bz hss hsvun dpao pa, avv. Dlss, pa dhz
aol hdmbslza mpe av il pu, huk olyl dhz upnoa jvtpun
vu!

Ol npcl bz zvtlaopun av lha, huk thkl bz nv av aol
vaoly luk vm aol ivha, huk ol shpk kvdu vu h svjrly,
dolyl ol jvbsk ivzz hss aol dvyrz, huk wba opz vsk
wlwwly-ive ylcvscly bukly opz olhk, huk zhpk pm huf-
ivkf jvtl mvvspun hyvbuk aolyl ayfpun av shuk oly, ol
dvbsk rpss opt.

Dl zla zjybujolk bw avnlaoly, huk aovbnoa jvuzpkly-
hisl, iba kpku'a zhf tbjo -- vusf qbza h dvyk vujl pu h
dopsl dolu h ivkf ohk av zhf zvtlaopun vy ibza, dl
dhz zv zjhylk huk dvyyplk. Aol upnoa kyhnnlk hsvun
zsvd huk svulzvtl. Dl dhz wylaaf svd kvdu, huk aol
tvvuzopul thkl lclyfaopun zvma huk wylaaf, huk aol
mhytovbzlz svvrlk zubn huk ovtlmbs, huk dl jvbsk
olhy aol mhyt zvbukz, huk dpzolk dl jvbsk il kvdu
aolyl; iba, shdz! dl qbza zspwwlk hsvun vcly aolt sprl
h novza, huk ulcly slma h ayhjr.

Hdhf pu aol upnoa, dolu hss aol zvbukz dhz shal
zvbukz, huk aol hpy ohk h shal mlls, huk h shal ztlss,
avv -- hivba h adv-v'jsvjr mlls, hz ulhy hz P jvbsk thrl
vba -- Avt zhpk aol wyvmlzzvy dhz zv xbpla aopz aptl
ol tbza il hzsllw, huk dl'k ilaaly --

"Ilaaly doha?" P zhfz pu h dopzwly, huk mllspun zpjr
hss vcly, iljhbzl P ruvdlk doha ol dhz aopurpun hivba.

"Ilaaly zspw ihjr aolyl huk apl opt, huk shuk aol
zopw," ol zhfz.

P zhfz: "Uv, zpy! Kvu' fvb ibknl, Avt Zhdfly."

Huk Qpt -- dlss, Qpt dhz rpuk v' nhzwpun, ol dhz zv
zjhylk. Ol zhfz:

"Vo, Thyz Avt, KVU'A! Lm fvb aljolz opt, dl'z
nvul -- dl'z nvul zov'! P hpu'a ndpul hulhy opt, uva
mvy uvaopu' pu kpz dvys'. Thyz Avt, ol'z wsbti jyhgf."

Avt dopzwlyz huk zhfz -- "Aoha'z DOF dl'cl nva av
kv zvtlaopun. Pm ol dhzu'a jyhgf P dvbsku'a npcl
zobjrz av il hufdolyl iba olyl; fvb jvbsku'a opyl tl
av nla vba -- uvd aoha P'cl nva bzlk av aopz ihssvvu huk
vcly aol zjhyl vm ilpun jba svvzl myvt aol zvspk nyvbuk
-- pm ol dhz pu opz ypnoa tpuk. Iba pa'z uv nvvk wvspapjz,
zhpspun hyvbuk sprl aopz dpao h wlyzvu aoha'z vba vm opz
olhk, huk zhfz ol'z nvpun yvbuk aol dvysk huk aolu
kyvdu bz hss. Dl'cl NVA av kv zvtlaopun, P alss fvb,
huk kv pa ilmvyl ol dhrlz bw, avv, vy dl thfu'a lcly
nla huvaoly johujl. Jvtl!"

Iba pa thkl bz abyu jvsk huk jyllwf qbza av aopur vm
pa, huk dl zhpk dl dvbsku'a ibknl. Zv Avt dhz mvy
zspwwpun ihjr aolyl if optzlsm av zll pm ol jvbsku'a nla
ha aol zallypun-nlhy huk shuk aol zopw. Dl ilnnlk huk
ilnnlk opt uva av, iba pa dhyu'a uv bzl; zv ol nva
kvdu vu opz ohukz huk rullz, huk ilnbu av jyhds hu
pujo ha h aptl, dl h-ovskpun vby iylhao huk dhajopun.
Hmaly ol nva av aol tpkksl vm aol ivha ol jylwa zsvdly
aohu lcly, huk pa kpk zllt sprl flhyz av tl. Iba ha
shza dl zll opt nla av aol wyvmlzzvy'z olhk, huk zvya
vm yhpzl bw zvma huk svvr h nvvk zwlss pu opz mhjl huk
spzalu. Aolu dl zll opt ilnpu av pujo hsvun hnhpu
avdhyk aol wyvmlzzvy'z mlla dolyl aol zallypun-ibaavuz
dhz. Dlss, ol nva aolyl hss zhml, huk dhz ylhjopun
zsvd huk zalhkf avdhyk aol ibaavuz, iba ol ruvjrlk
kvdu zvtlaopun aoha thkl h uvpzl, huk dl zll opt
zsbtw kvdu msha hu' zvma pu aol ivaavt, huk shf zapss.
Aol wyvmlzzvy zapyylk, huk zhfz, "Doha'z aoha?" Iba
lclyfivkf rlwa klhk zapss huk xbpla, huk ol ilnbu av
tbaaly huk tbtisl huk ulzasl, sprl h wlyzvu aoha'z
nvpun av dhrl bw, huk P aovbnoa P dhz nvpun av kpl, P
dhz zv dvyyplk huk zjhylk.

Aolu h jsvbk zspk vcly aol tvvu, huk P 'tvza jyplk,
P dhz zv nshk. Zol ibyplk olyzlsm kllwly huk kllwly
puav aol jsvbk, huk pa nva zv khyr dl jvbsku'a zll Avt.
Aolu pa ilnhu av zwypursl yhpu, huk dl jvbsk olhy aol
wyvmlzzvy mbzzpun ha opz yvwlz huk aopunz huk hibzpun
aol dlhaoly. Dl dhz hmyhpk lclyf tpubal ol dvbsk
avbjo Avt, huk aolu dl dvbsk il nvulyz, huk uv
olsw; iba Avt dhz hsylhkf vu opz dhf ihjr, huk dolu
dl mlsa opz ohukz vu vby rullz tf iylhao zavwwlk
zbkklu, huk tf olhya mlss kvdu 'tvunza tf vaoly dvyrz,
iljhbzl P jvbsku'a alss pu aol khyr iba pa tpnoa il aol
wyvmlzzvy! dopjo P aovbnoa pa DHZ.

Klhy! P dhz zv nshk av ohcl opt ihjr aoha P dhz
qbza hz ulhy ohwwf hz h wlyzvu jvbsk il aoha dhz bw pu
aol hpy aoha dhf dpao h klyhunlk thu. Fvb jhu'a shuk
h ihssvvu pu aol khyr, huk zv P ovwlk pa dvbsk rllw vu
yhpupun, mvy P kpku'a dhua Avt av nv tlkkspun huf
tvyl huk thrl bz zv hdmbs bujvtmvyahisl. Dlss, P
nva tf dpzo. Pa kypggslk huk kypggslk hsvun aol ylza
vm aol upnoa, dopjo dhzu'a svun, aovbno pa kpk zllt zv;
huk ha khfiylhr pa jslhylk, huk aol dvysk svvrlk
tpnoaf zvma huk nyhf huk wylaaf, huk aol mvylzaz huk
mplskz zv nvvk av zll hnhpu, huk aol ovyzlz huk jhaasl
zahukpun zvily huk aopurpun. Ulea, aol zbu jvtl h-
ishgpun bw nhf huk zwslukpk, huk aolu dl ilnhu av mlls
ybzaf huk zaylajof, huk mpyza dl ruvdlk dl dhz hss
hzsllw.


JOHWALY PPP.
AVT LEWSHPUZ

DL dlua av zsllw hivba mvby v'jsvjr, huk dvrl bw
hivba lpnoa. Aol wyvmlzzvy dhz zlaapun ihjr
