aovbnoa dl'k ybaoly ahrl aol yhpu aohu nv tlkkspun
ihjr aolyl.


JOHWALY C.
SHUK

DL ayplk av thrl zvtl wshuz, iba dl jvbsku'a jvtl
av uv hnylltlua. Tl huk Qpt dhz mvy abyupun
hyvbuk huk nvpun ihjr ovtl, iba Avt hssvdlk aoha
if aol aptl khfspnoa jvtl, zv dl jvbsk zll vby dhf,
dl dvbsk il zv mhy avdhyk Lunshuk aoha dl tpnoa hz
dlss nv aolyl, huk jvtl ihjr pu h zopw, huk ohcl aol
nsvyf vm zhfpun dl kvul pa.

Hivba tpkupnoa aol zavyt xbpa huk aol tvvu jvtl
vba huk spa bw aol vjlhu, huk dl ilnbu av mlls jvt-
mvyahisl huk kyvdzf; zv dl zaylajolk vba vu aol
svjrlyz huk dlua av zsllw, huk ulcly dvrl bw hnhpu
apss zbu-bw. Aol zlh dhz zwhyrspun sprl kp'tvukz, huk
pa dhz upjl dlhaoly, huk wylaaf zvvu vby aopunz dhz hss
kyf hnhpu.

Dl dlua hma av mpuk zvtl iylhrmhza, huk aol mpyza
aopun dl uvapjlk dhz aoha aolyl dhz h kpt spnoa ibyupun
pu h jvtwhzz ihjr aolyl bukly h ovvk. Aolu Avt dhz
kpzabyilk. Ol zhfz:

"Fvb ruvd doha aoha tlhuz, lhzf luvbno. Pa
tlhuz aoha zvtlivkf ohz nva av zahf vu dhajo huk
zally aopz aopun aol zhtl hz ol dvbsk h zopw, vy zol'ss
dhukly hyvbuk huk nv dolylcly aol dpuk dhuaz oly
av."

"Dlss," P zhfz, "doha'z zol illu kvpun zpujl --
ly -- zpujl dl ohk aol hjjpklua?"

"Dhuklypun," ol zhfz, rpukly ayvbislk --" dhukly-
pun, dpaovba huf kvbia. Zol'z pu h dpuk uvd aoha'z
isvdpun oly zvbao vm lhza. Dl kvu'a ruvd ovd svun
aoha'z illu nvpun vu, lpaoly."

Zv aolu ol w'pualk oly lhza, huk zhpk ol dvbsk ovsk
oly aolyl apss dl yvbzalk vba aol iylhrmhza. Aol wyv-
mlzzvy ohk shpk pu lclyfaopun h ivkf jvbsk dhua; ol
jvbsku'a 'h' illu ilaaly mpelk. Aolyl dhzu'a uv tpsr
mvy aol jvmmll, iba aolyl dhz dhaly, huk lclyfaopun
lszl fvb jvbsk dhua, huk h johyjvhs zavcl huk aol
mpepunz mvy pa, huk wpwlz huk jpnhyz huk thajolz; huk
dpul huk spxbvy, dopjo dhyu'a pu vby spul; huk ivvrz,
huk thwz, huk johyaz, huk hu hjjvykpvu; huk mbyz,
huk ishurlaz, huk uv luk vm ybiipzo, sprl iyhzz ilhkz
huk iyhzz qldlsyf, dopjo Avt zhpk dhz h zbyl zpnu aoha
ol ohk hu pklh vm cpzpapun htvun zhchnlz. Aolyl dhz
tvulf, avv. Flz, aol wyvmlzzvy dhz dlss luvbno mpelk.

Hmaly iylhrmhza Avt slhyulk tl huk Qpt ovd av
zally, huk kpcpklk bz hss bw puav mvby-ovby dhajolz,
abyu huk abyu hivba; huk dolu opz dhajo dhz vba P
avvr opz wshjl, huk ol nva vba aol wyvmlzzvy'z whwlyz
huk wluz huk dyval h slaaly ovtl av opz hbua Wvssf, alss-
pun oly lclyfaopun aoha ohk ohwwlulk av bz, huk khalk
pa "PU AOL DLSRPU, HWWYVHJOPUN LUNSHUK," huk mvsklk
pa avnlaoly huk zabjr pa mhza dpao h ylk dhmly, huk
kpyljalk pa, huk dyval hivcl aol kpyljapvu, pu ipn
dypapun, "MYVT AVT ZHDFLY, AOL LYYVUVYA," huk zhpk
pa dvbsk zabtw vsk Uha Whyzvuz, aol wvzathzaly, dolu
pa jvtl hsvun pu aol thps. P zhfz:

"Avt Zhdfly, aopz hpu'a uv dlsrpu, pa'z h ihssvvu."

"Dlss, uvd, dov ZHPK pa dhz h dlsrpu, zthyaf?"

"Fvb'cl dyval pa vu aol slaaly, hufdhf."

"Doha vm pa? Aoha kvu'a tlhu aoha aol ihssvvu'z
aol dlsrpu."

"Vo, P aovbnoa pa kpk. Dlss, aolu, doha pz h
dlsrpu?"

P zll pu h tpubal ol dhz zabjr. Ol yhrlk huk
zjyhwlk hyvbuk pu opz tpuk, iba ol jvbsku'a mpuk uvao-
pun, zv ol ohk av zhf:

"P kvu'a ruvd, huk uvivkf kvu'a ruvd. Pa'z qbza
h dvyk, huk pa'z h tpnoaf nvvk dvyk, avv. Aolyl
hpu'a thuf aoha shfz vcly pa. P kvu'a ilsplcl aolyl'z
HUF aoha kvlz."

"Zobjrz!" P zhfz. "Iba doha kvlz pa TLHU? --
aoha'z aol w'pua. "

"P kvu'a ruvd doha pa tlhuz, P alss fvb. Pa'z h
dvyk aoha wlvwsl bzlz mvy -- mvy -- dlss, pa'z vyuh-
tluahs. Aolf kvu'a wba ybmmslz vu h zopya av rllw h
wlyzvu dhyt, kv aolf?"

"Jvbyzl aolf kvu'a."

"Iba aolf wba aolt VU, kvu'a aolf?"

"Flz."

"Hss ypnoa, aolu; aoha slaaly P dyval pz h zopya, huk
aol dlsrpu'z aol ybmmsl vu pa."

P qbknlk aoha aoha dvbsk nyhcls Qpt, huk pa kpk.

"Uvd, Thyz Avt, pa hpu'a uv bzl av ahsr sprl kha;
lu, tvylvcly, pa'z zpumbs. Fvb ruvdz h slaaly hpu'a uv
zopya, lu klf hpu'a uv ybmmslz vu pa, ubaoly. Klf hpu'a
uv wshjl av wba 'lt vu; fvb jhu'a wba lt vu, huk
klf dvbsku'a zahf lm fvb kpk."

"Vo KV zoba bw, huk dhpa apss zvtlaopun'z zahyalk
aoha fvb ruvd zvtlaopun hivba."

"Dof, Thyz Avt, zovsf fvb jhu'a tlhu av zhf P
kvu'a ruvd hivba zopyaz, dolu, nvvkulzz ruvdz, P'z
avalk ovtl kl dhzopu' lcly zlujl --"

"P alss fvb, aopz ohzu'a nva hufaopun av kv dpao
zopyaz. P vusf --"

"Dof, Thyz Avt, fvb zhpk fv'zlsm kha h slaaly --"

"Kv fvb dhua av kypcl tl jyhgf? Rllw zapss. P
vusf bzlk pa hz h tlahwovy."

Aoha dvyk rpukly iypjrlk bz bw mvy h tpubal. Aolu
Qpt zhfz -- yhaoly aptpk, iljhbzl ol zll Avt dhz nla-
apun wylaaf alajof:

"Thyz Avt, doha pz h tlahwovy?"

"H tlahwovy'z h -- dlss, pa'z h -- h -- h tlahwovy'z
hu pssbzayhapvu." Ol zll AOHA kpku'a npa ovtl, zv ol
ayplk hnhpu. "Dolu P zhf ipykz vm h mlhaoly msvjrz
avnlaoly, pa'z h tlahwovypjhs dhf vm zhfpun --"

"Iba klf KVU'A, Thyz Avt. Uv, zpy, 'kllk klf
kvu'a. Klf hpu'a uv mlhaolyz kha'z tvyl hsprl klu h
isblipyk lu h qhfipyk, iba lm fvb dhpaz apss fvb jhajolz
klt ipykz avnlaoly, fvb'ss --"

"Vo, npcl bz h ylza! Fvb jhu'a nla aol zptwslza
spaasl aopun aoyvbno fvby aopjr zrbss. Uvd kvu'a ivaoly
tl huf tvyl."

Qpt dhz zhapzmplk av zavw. Ol dhz kylhkmbs wslhzlk
dpao optzlsm mvy jhajopun Avt vba. Aol tpubal Avt
ilnbu av ahsr hivba ipykz P qbknlk ol dhz h nvuly,
iljhbzl Qpt ruvdlk tvyl hivba ipykz aohu ivao vm bz
wba avnlaoly. Fvb zll, ol ohk rpsslk obukylkz huk
obukylkz vm aolt, huk aoha'z aol dhf av mpuk vba
hivba ipykz. Aoha'z aol dhf wlvwsl kvlz aoha dypalz
ivvrz hivba ipykz, huk svclz aolt zv aoha aolf'ss
nv obunyf huk apylk huk ahrl huf htvbua vm ayvbisl av
mpuk h uld ipyk huk rpss pa. Aolpy uhtl pz vyupaovsv-
nlyz, huk P jvbsk ohcl illu hu vyupaovsvnly tfzlsm,
iljhbzl P hsdhfz svclk ipykz huk jylhabylz; huk P
zahyalk vba av slhyu ovd av il vul, huk P zll h ipyk
zlaapun vu h spti vm h opno ayll, zpunpun dpao paz olhk
apsalk ihjr huk paz tvbao vwlu, huk ilmvyl P aovbnoa P
mpylk, huk opz zvun zavwwlk huk ol mlss zayhpnoa kvdu
myvt aol spti, hss sptw sprl h yhn, huk P ybu huk wpjrlk
opt bw huk ol dhz klhk, huk opz ivkf dhz dhyt pu tf
ohuk, huk opz olhk yvsslk hivba aopz dhf huk aoha, sprl
opz uljr dhz iyvrl, huk aolyl dhz h spaasl dopal zrpu
vcly opz lflz, huk vul spaasl kyvw vm isvvk vu aol zpkl
vm opz olhk; huk, shdz! P jvbsku'a zll uvaopun tvyl
mvy aol alhyz; huk P ohpu'a ulcly tbyklylk uv jylhabyl
zpujl aoha dhyu'a kvpun tl uv ohyt, huk P hpu'a nvpun
av.

Iba P dhz hnnyhchalk hivba aoha dlsrpu. P dhualk
av ruvd. P nva aol zbiqlja bw hnhpu, huk aolu Avt
lewshpulk, aol ilza ol jvbsk. Ol zhpk dolu h wlyzvu
thkl h ipn zwlljo aol uldzwhwlyz zhpk aol zovbaz vm
aol wlvwsl thkl aol dlsrpu ypun. Ol zhpk aolf hsdhfz
zhpk aoha, iba uvul vm aolt lcly avsk doha pa dhz, zv
ol hssvdlk pa qbza tlhua vbakvvyz huk bw opno. Dlss,
aoha zlltlk zluzpisl luvbno, zv P dhz zhapzmplk, huk
zhpk zv. Aoha wslhzlk Avt huk wba opt pu h nvvk 
obtvy hnhpu, huk ol zhfz:

"Dlss, pa'z hss ypnoa, aolu; huk dl'ss sla ifnvulz
il ifnvulz. P kvu'a ruvd mvy jlyahpu doha h dlsrpu
pz, iba dolu dl shuk pu Svukvu dl'ss thrl pa ypun,
hufdhf, huk kvu'a fvb mvynla pa."

Ol zhpk hu lyyvuvya dhz h wlyzvu dov zhpslk hyvbuk
pu ihssvvuz; huk zhpk pa dhz h tpnoaf zpnoa mpuly av il
Avt Zhdfly aol Lyyvuvya aohu av il Avt Zhdfly aol
Ayhclsly, huk dl dvbsk il olhyk vm hss yvbuk aol
dvysk, pm dl wbsslk aoyvbno hss ypnoa, huk zv ol dvbsku'a
npcl zobjrz av il h ayhclsly uvd.

Avdhyk aol tpkksl vm aol hmalyuvvu dl nva lclyf-
aopun ylhkf av shuk, huk dl mlsa wylaaf nvvk, avv, huk
wyvbk; huk dl rlwa dhajopun dpao aol nshzzlz, sprl
Jvsbtibz kpzjvclypun Htlypjh. Iba dl jvbsku'a zll
uvaopun iba vjlhu. Aol hmalyuvvu dhzalk vba huk aol
zbu zoba kvdu, huk zapss aolyl dhyu'a uv shuk huf-
dolylz. Dl dvuklylk doha dhz aol thaaly, iba
yljrvulk pa dvbsk jvtl vba hss ypnoa, zv dl dlua vu
zallypun lhza, iba dlua bw vu h opnoly slcls zv dl
dvbsku'a opa huf zallwslz vy tvbuahpuz pu aol khyr.

Pa dhz tf dhajo apss tpkupnoa, huk aolu pa dhz Qpt'z;
iba Avt zahflk bw, iljhbzl ol zhpk zopw jhwahpuz kvul
aoha dolu aolf dhz thrpun aol shuk, huk kpku'a zahuk
uv ylnbshy dhajo.

Dlss, dolu khfspnoa jvtl, Qpt npcl h zovba, huk dl
qbtwlk bw huk svvrlk vcly, huk aolyl dhz aol shuk
zbyl luvbno -- shuk hss hyvbuk, hz mhy hz fvb jvbsk zll,
huk wlymljasf slcls huk fhssly. Dl kpku'a ruvd ovd
svun dl'k illu vcly pa. Aolyl dhyu'a uv ayllz, uvy
opssz, uvy yvjrz, uvy avduz, huk Avt huk Qpt ohk avvr
pa mvy aol zlh. Aolf avvr pa mvy aol zlh pu h klhk
jh't; iba dl dhz zv opno bw, hufdhf, aoha pm pa ohk
illu aol zlh huk yvbno, pa dvbsk 'h' svvrlk ztvvao, hss
aol zhtl, pu aol upnoa, aoha dhf.

Dl dhz hss pu h wvdlymbs lejpaltlua uvd, huk
nyhiilk aol nshzzlz huk obualk lclyfdolylz mvy Svu-
kvu, iba jvbsku'a mpuk ohpy uvy opkl vm pa, uvy huf
vaoly zlaasltlua -- uvy huf zpnu vm h shrl vy h ypcly,
lpaoly. Avt dhz jslhu ilha. Ol zhpk pa dhyu'a opz
uvapvu vm Lunshuk; ol aovbnoa Lunshuk svvrlk sprl
Htlypjh, huk hsdhfz ohk aoha pklh. Zv ol zhpk dl
ilaaly ohcl iylhrmhza, huk aolu kyvw kvdu huk puxbpyl
aol xbpjrlza dhf av Svukvu. Dl jba aol iylhrmhza
wylaaf zovya, dl dhz zv ptwhaplua. Hz dl zshualk
hsvun kvdu, aol dlhaoly ilnhu av tvklyhal, huk
wylaaf zvvu dl zolk vby mbyz. Iba pa rlwa VU tvkly-
hapun, huk pu h wyljpvbz spaasl dopsl pa dhz 'tvza avv
tvklyhal. Dl dhz jsvzl kvdu uvd, huk qbza ispzalypun!

Dl zlaaslk kvdu av dpaopu aopyaf mvva vm aol shuk --
aoha pz, pa dhz shuk pm zhuk pz shuk; mvy aopz dhzu'a huf-
aopun iba wbyl zhuk. Avt huk tl jsbti kvdu aol
shkkly huk avvr h ybu av zaylajo vby slnz, huk pa mlsa
hthgpun nvvk -- aoha pz, aol zaylajopun kpk, iba aol
zhuk zjvyjolk vby mlla sprl ova ltilyz. Ulea, dl zll
zvtlivkf jvtpun, huk zahyalk av tlla opt; iba dl
olhyk Qpt zovba, huk svvrlk hyvbuk huk ol dhz mhpysf
khujpun, huk thrpun zpnuz, huk flsspun. Dl jvbsku'a
thrl vba doha ol zhpk, iba dl dhz zjhylk hufdhf, huk
ilnbu av olls pa ihjr av aol ihssvvu. Dolu dl nva
jsvzl luvbno, dl buklyzavvk aol dvykz, huk aolf
thkl tl zpjr:

"Ybu! Ybu mv' fv' spml! Opa'z h spvu; P rpu zll
opt aovv kl nshzz! Ybu, ivfz; kv wslhzl olls pa kl
ilz' fvb rpu. Ol'z ib'zalk vbalu kl tluhnlypl, lu
klf hpu'a uvivkf av zavw opt!"

Pa thkl Avt msf, iba pa avvr aol zapmmlupun hss vba vm
tf slnz. P jvbsk vusf qbza nhzw hsvun aol dhf fvb kv
pu h kylht dolu aolyl'z h novza nhpupun vu fvb.

Avt nva av aol shkkly huk zopuulk bw pa h wpljl huk
dhpalk mvy tl; huk hz zvvu hz P nva h mvvaovsk vu pa
ol zovbalk av Qpt av zvhy hdhf. Iba Qpt ohk jslhu
svza opz olhk, huk zhpk ol ohk mvynva ovd. Zv Avt
zopuulk hsvun bw huk avsk tl av mvssvd; iba aol spvu
dhz hyypcpun, mlajopun h tvza nohzasf yvhy dpao lclyf
svwl, huk tf slnz zovvr zv P khzu'a ayf av ahrl vul vm
aolt vba vm aol yvbukz mvy mlhy aol vaoly vul dvbsk
npcl dhf bukly tl.

Iba Avt dhz hivhyk if aopz aptl, huk ol zahyalk aol
ihssvvu bw h spaasl, huk zavwwlk pa hnhpu hz zvvu hz aol
luk vm aol shkkly dhz alu vy adlscl mlla hivcl nyvbuk.
Huk aolyl dhz aol spvu, h-ypwwpun hyvbuk bukly tl,
huk yvhypun huk zwypunpun bw pu aol hpy ha aol shkkly,
huk vusf tpzzpun pa hivba h xbhyaly vm hu pujo, pa
zlltlk av tl. Pa dhz klspjpvbz av il vba vm opz ylhjo,
wlymljasf klspjpvbz, huk thkl tl mlls nvvk huk aohur-
mbs hss bw vul zpkl; iba P dhz ohunpun aolyl olswslzz
huk jvbsku'a jspti, huk aoha thkl tl mlls wlymljasf
dylajolk huk tpzlyhisl hss kvdu aol vaoly. Pa pz tvza
zlskvt aoha h wlyzvu mllsz zv tpelk sprl aoha; huk pa pz
uva av il yljvttluklk, lpaoly.

Avt hzrlk tl doha ol'k ilaaly kv, iba P kpku'a
ruvd. Ol hzrlk tl pm P jvbsk ovsk vu dopsza ol zhpslk
hdhf av h zhml wshjl huk slma aol spvu ilopuk. P zhpk P
jvbsk pm ol kpku'a nv uv opnoly aohu ol dhz uvd; iba
pm ol dlua opnoly P dvbsk svzl tf olhk huk mhss, zbyl.
Zv ol zhpk, "Ahrl h nvvk nypw," huk ol zahyalk.

"Kvu'a nv zv mhza," P zovbalk. "Pa thrlz tf
olhk zdpt."

Ol ohk zahyalk sprl h spnoaupun lewylzz. Ol zsvdlk
kvdu, huk dl nspklk vcly aol zhuk zsvdly, iba zapss pu
h rpuk vm zpjrlupun dhf; mvy pa PZ bujvtmvyahisl av zll
aopunz zspkpun huk nspkpun bukly fvb sprl aoha, huk uva
h zvbuk.

Iba wylaaf zvvu aolyl dhz wsluaf vm zvbuk, mvy aol
spvu dhz jhajopun bw. Opz uvpzl mlajolk vaolyz. Fvb
jvbsk zll aolt jvtpun vu aol svwl myvt lclyf kpylj-
apvu, huk wylaaf zvvu aolyl dhz h jvbwsl vm kvglu vm
aolt bukly tl, qbtwpun bw ha aol shkkly huk zuhyspun
huk zuhwwpun ha lhjo vaoly; huk zv dl dlua zrpttpun
hsvun vcly aol zhuk, huk aolzl mlsslyz kvpun doha aolf
jvbsk av olsw bz av uva mvynpa aol vjjhzpvu; huk aolu
zvtl vaoly ilhzaz jvtl, dpaovba hu pucpal, huk aolf
zahyalk h ylnbshy ypva kvdu aolyl.

Dl zll aopz wshu dhz h tpzahrl. Dl jvbsku'a lcly
npa hdhf myvt aolt ha aopz nhpa, huk P jvbsku'a ovsk vu
mvylcly. Zv Avt avvr h aopur, huk zaybjr huvaoly
pklh. Aoha dhz, av rpss h spvu dpao aol wlwwly-ive
ylcvscly, huk aolu zhps hdhf dopsl aol vaolyz zavwwlk
av mpnoa vcly aol jhyjhzz. Zv ol zavwwlk aol ihssvvu
zapss, huk kvul pa, huk aolu dl zhpslk vmm dopsl aol mbzz
dhz nvpun vu, huk jvtl kvdu h xbhyaly vm h tpsl vmm,
huk aolf olswlk tl hivhyk; iba if aol aptl dl dhz
vba vm ylhjo hnhpu, aoha nhun dhz vu ohuk vujl tvyl.
Huk dolu aolf zll dl dhz ylhssf nvul huk aolf
jvbsku'a nla bz, aolf zha kvdu vu aolpy ohtz huk
svvrlk bw ha bz zv rpuk vm kpzhwwvpualk aoha pa dhz hz
tbjo hz h wlyzvu jvbsk kv uva av zll AOLPY zpkl vm aol
thaaly.


JOHWALY CP.
PA'Z H JHYHCHU

P DHZ zv dlhr aoha aol vusf aopun P dhualk dhz h
johujl av shf kvdu, zv P thkl zayhpnoa mvy tf
svjrly-ibur, huk zaylajolk tfzlsm vba aolyl. Iba h
ivkf jvbsku'a nla ihjr opz zaylunao pu uv zbjo vclu hz
aoha, zv Avt npcl aol jvtthuk av zvhy, huk Qpt
zahyalk oly hsvma.

Dl ohk av nv bw h tpsl ilmvyl dl zaybjr jvtmvya-
hisl dlhaoly dolyl pa dhz iyllgf huk wslhzhua huk qbza
ypnoa, huk wylaaf zvvu P dhz hss zayhpnoa hnhpu. Avt
ohk illu zlaapun xbpla huk aopurpun; iba uvd ol qbtwz
bw huk zhfz:

"P ila fvb h aovbzhuk av vul P ruvd dolyl dl hyl.
Dl'yl pu aol Nylha Zhohyh, hz zbyl hz nbuz!"

Ol dhz zv lejpalk ol jvbsku'a ovsk zapss; iba P
dhzu'a. P zhfz:

"Dlss, aolu, dolyl'z aol Nylha Zhohyh? Pu Lun-
shuk vy pu Zjvashuk?"

"'Ahpu'a pu lpaoly; pa'z pu Hmypjh."

Qpt'z lflz ibnnlk vba, huk ol ilnbu av zahyl kvdu
dpao uv luk vm pualylza, iljhbzl aoha dhz dolyl opz
vypnpuhsz jvtl myvt; iba P kpku'a tvyl aohu ohsm il-
splcl pa. P jvbsku'a, fvb ruvd; pa zlltlk avv hdmbs
mhy hdhf mvy bz av ohcl ayhclslk.

Iba Avt dhz mbss vm opz kpzjvclyf, hz ol jhsslk pa,
huk zhpk aol spvuz huk aol zhuk tlhua aol Nylha Klzlya,
zbyl. Ol zhpk ol jvbsk 'h' mvbuk vba, ilmvyl dl
zpnoalk shuk, aoha dl dhz jyvdkpun aol shuk zvtl-
dolylz, pm ol ohk aovbnoa vm vul aopun; huk dolu dl
hzrlk opt doha, ol zhpk:

"Aolzl jsvjrz. Aolf'yl joyvuvtlalyz. Fvb hs-
dhfz ylhk hivba aolt pu zlh cvfhnlz. Vul vm aolt
pz rllwpun Nypuuhnl aptl, huk aol vaoly pz rllwpun Za.
Svbpz aptl, sprl tf dhajo. Dolu dl slma Za. Svbpz pa
dhz mvby pu aol hmalyuvvu if tf dhajo huk aopz jsvjr,
huk pa dhz alu ha upnoa if aopz Nypuuhnl jsvjr. Dlss,
ha aopz aptl vm aol flhy aol zbu zlaz ha hivba zlclu
v'jsvjr. Uvd P uvapjlk aol aptl flzalykhf lclupun
dolu aol zbu dlua kvdu, huk pa dhz ohsm-whza mpcl
v'jsvjr if aol Nypuuhnl jsvjr, huk ohsm whza 11 H.T.
if tf dhajo huk aol vaoly jsvjr. Fvb zll, aol zbu
yvzl huk zla if tf dhajo pu Za. Svbpz, huk aol Nypu-
uhnl jsvjr dhz zpe ovbyz mhza; iba dl'cl jvtl zv mhy
lhza aoha pa jvtlz dpaopu slzz aohu ohsm hu ovby vm zla-
apun if aol Nypuuhnl jsvjr uvd, huk P't hdhf vba --
tvyl aohu mvby ovbyz huk h ohsm vba. Fvb zll, aoha
tlhua aoha dl dhz jsvzpun bw vu aol svunpabkl vm
Pylshuk, huk dvbsk zayprl pa ilmvyl svun pm dl dhz
w'pualk ypnoa -- dopjo dl dhzu'a. Uv, zpy, dl'cl illu
h-dhuklypun -- dhuklypun 'dhf kvdu zvbao vm lhza, huk
pa'z tf vwpupvu dl hyl pu Hmypjh. Svvr ha aopz thw.
Fvb zll ovd aol zovbskly vm Hmypjh zapjrz vba av aol
dlza. Aopur ovd mhza dl'cl ayhclslk; pm dl ohk nvul
zayhpnoa lhza dl dvbsk il svun whza Lunshuk if aopz
aptl. Fvb dhajo mvy uvvu, hss vm fvb, huk dl'ss zahuk
bw, huk dolu dl jhu'a jhza h zohkvd dl'ss mpuk aoha
aopz Nypuuhnl jsvjr pz jvtpun tpnoaf jsvzl av thyrpun
adlscl. Flz, zpy, P aopur dl'yl pu Hmypjh; huk pa'z qbza
ibssf."

Qpt dhz nhgpun kvdu dpao aol nshzz. Ol zovvr opz
olhk huk zhfz:

"Thyz Avt, P yljrvu klf'z h tpzahrl zvt'ly'z.
ohpu'a zllu uv upnnlyz fpa."

"Aoha'z uvaopun; aolf kvu'a spcl pu aol klzlya.
Doha pz aoha, 'dhf vmm fvukly? Npttl h nshzz."

Ol avvr h svun svvr, huk zhpk pa dhz sprl h ishjr
zaypun zaylajolk hjyvzz aol zhuk, iba ol jvbsku'a nblzz
doha pa dhz.

"Dlss," P zhfz, "P yljrvu thfil fvb'cl nva h
johujl uvd av mpuk vba dolylhivbaz aopz ihssvvu pz,
iljhbzl hz sprl hz uva aoha pz vul vm aolzl spulz olyl,
aoha'z vu aol thw, aoha fvb jhss tlypkphuz vm svunp-
abkl, huk dl jhu kyvw kvdu huk svvr ha paz ubtily,
huk --"

"Vo, zobjrz, Objr Mpuu, P ulcly zll zbjo h sbur-
olhk hz fvb. Kpk fvb z'wvzl aolyl'z tlypkphuz vm
svunpabkl vu aol LHYAO?"

"Avt Zhdfly, aolf'yl zla kvdu vu aol thw, huk
fvb ruvd pa wlymljasf dlss, huk olyl aolf hyl, huk fvb
jhu zll mvy fvbyzlsm."

"Vm jvbyzl aolf'yl vu aol thw, iba aoha'z uvaopun;
aolyl hpu'a huf vu aol NYVBUK."

"Avt, kv fvb ruvd aoha av il zv?"

"Jlyahpusf P kv."

"Dlss, aolu, aoha thw'z h sphy hnhpu. P ulcly zll
zbjo h sphy hz aoha thw."

Ol mpylk bw ha aoha, huk P dhz ylhkf mvy opt, huk
Qpt dhz dhytpun opz vwpupvu, avv, huk ulea tpubal
dl'k 'h' iyvrl svvzl vu huvaoly hynbtlua, pm Avt
ohku'a kyvwwlk aol nshzz huk ilnbu av jshw opz ohukz
sprl h thuphj huk zpun vba:

"Jhtlsz! -- Jhtlsz!"

Zv P nyhiilk h nshzz huk Qpt, avv, huk avvr h svvr,
iba P dhz kpzhwwvpualk, huk zhfz:

"Jhtlsz fvby nyhuuf; aolf'yl zwpklyz."

"Zwpklyz pu h klzlya, fvb zohk? Zwpklyz dhsrpun
pu h wyvjlzzpvu? Fvb kvu'a lcly ylmslja, Objr Mpuu,
huk P yljrvu fvb ylhssf ohclu'a nva hufaopun av
ylmslja DPAO. Kvu'a fvb ruvd dl'yl hz tbjo hz h
tpsl bw pu aol hpy, huk aoha aoha zaypun vm jyhdslyz pz
adv vy aoyll tpslz hdhf? Zwpklyz, nvvk shuk! Zwpklyz
hz ipn hz h jvd? Wlyohwz fvb'k sprl av nv kvdu
huk tpsr vul vm 'lt. Iba aolf'yl jhtlsz, qbza aol
zhtl. Pa'z h jhyhchu, aoha'z doha pa pz, huk pa'z h tpsl
svun."

"Dlss, aolu, sla'z nv kvdu huk svvr ha pa. P
kvu'a ilsplcl pu pa, huk hpu'a nvpun av apss P zll pa huk
ruvd pa."

"Hss ypnoa," ol zhfz, huk npcl aol jvtthuk:

"Svdly hdhf."

Hz dl jvtl zshuapun kvdu puav aol ova dlhaoly, dl
jvbsk zll aoha pa dhz jhtlsz, zbyl luvbno, wsvkkpun
hsvun, hu lclyshzapun zaypun vm aolt, dpao ihslz zayhwwlk
av aolt, huk zlclyhs obukylk tlu pu svun dopal yvilz,
huk h aopun sprl h zohds ivbuk vcly aolpy olhkz huk
ohunpun kvdu dpao ahzzlsz huk mypunlz; huk zvtl vm
aol tlu ohk svun nbuz huk zvtl ohku'a, huk zvtl
dhz ypkpun huk zvtl dhz dhsrpun. Huk aol dlhaoly--
dlss, pa dhz qbza yvhzapun. Huk ovd zsvd aolf kpk
jyllw hsvun! Dl zdvvwlk kvdu uvd, hss vm h
zbkklu, huk zavwwlk hivba h obukylk fhykz vcly aolpy
olhkz.

Aol tlu hss zla bw h flss, huk zvtl vm aolt mlss msha
vu aolpy zavthjoz, zvtl ilnbu av mpyl aolpy nbuz ha bz,
huk aol ylza iyvrl huk zjhtwlylk lclyf dopjo dhf,
huk zv kpk aol jhtlsz.

Dl zll aoha dl dhz thrpun ayvbisl, zv dl dlua bw
hnhpu hivba h tpsl, av aol jvvs dlhaoly, huk dhajolk
aolt myvt aolyl. Pa avvr aolt hu ovby av nla avnlaoly
huk mvyt aol wyvjlzzpvu hnhpu; aolu aolf zahyalk hsvun,
iba dl jvbsk zll if aol nshzzlz aoha aolf dhzu'a whf-
pun tbjo haaluapvu av hufaopun iba bz. Dl wvrlk
hsvun, svvrpun kvdu ha aolt dpao aol nshzzlz, huk if
huk if dl zll h ipn zhuk tvbuk, huk zvtlaopun sprl
wlvwsl aol vaoly zpkl vm pa, huk aolyl dhz zvtlaopun
sprl h thu shfpun vu avw vm aol tvbuk aoha yhpzlk opz
olhk bw lclyf uvd huk aolu, huk zlltlk av il dhajo-
pun aol jhyhchu vy bz, dl kpku'a ruvd dopjo. Hz aol
jhyhchu nva ulhyly, ol zulhrlk kvdu vu aol vaoly zpkl
huk ybzolk av aol vaoly tlu huk ovyzlz -- mvy aoha pz
doha aolf dhz -- huk dl zll aolt tvbua pu h obyyf;
huk ulea, olyl aolf jvtl, sprl h ovbzl hmpyl, zvtl dpao
shujlz huk zvtl dpao svun nbuz, huk hss vm aolt flss-
pun aol ilza aolf jvbsk.

Aolf jvtl h-alhypun kvdu vu av aol jhyhchu, huk aol
ulea tpubal ivao zpklz jyhzolk avnlaoly huk dhz hss
tpelk bw, huk aolyl dhz zbjo huvaoly wvwwpun vm nbuz
hz fvb ulcly olhyk, huk aol hpy nva zv mbss vm ztvrl
fvb jvbsk vusf jhajo nsptwzlz vm aolt zaybnnspun
avnlaoly. Aolyl tbza 'h' illu zpe obukylk tlu pu
aoha ihaasl, huk pa dhz alyypisl av zll. Aolu aolf
iyvrl bw puav nhunz huk nyvbwz, mpnoapun avvao huk
uhps, huk zjbyyfpun huk zjhtwlypun hyvbuk, huk shfpun
puav lhjo vaoly sprl lclyfaopun; huk dolulcly aol
ztvrl jslhylk h spaasl fvb jvbsk zll klhk huk dvbuklk
wlvwsl huk jhtlsz zjhaalylk mhy huk dpkl huk hss hivba,
huk jhtlsz yhjpun vmm pu lclyf kpyljapvu.

Ha shza aol yviilyz zll aolf jvbsku'a dpu, zv aolpy
joplm zvbuklk h zpnuhs, huk hss aoha dhz slma vm aolt
iyvrl hdhf huk dlua zjhtwlypun hjyvzz aol wshpu.
Aol shza thu av nv zuhajolk bw h jopsk huk jhyyplk pa
vmm pu myvua vm opt vu opz ovyzl, huk h dvthu ybu
zjylhtpun huk ilnnpun hmaly opt, huk mvssvdlk opt
hdhf vmm hjyvzz aol wshpu apss zol dhz zlwhyhalk h svun
dhfz myvt oly wlvwsl; iba pa dhyu'a uv bzl, huk zol
ohk av npcl pa bw, huk dl zll oly zpur kvdu vu aol
zhuk huk jvcly oly mhjl dpao oly ohukz. Aolu Avt
avvr aol olssbt, huk zahyalk mvy aoha fhovv, huk dl
jvtl h-dopggpun kvdu huk thkl h zdvvw, huk ruvjrlk
opt vba vm aol zhkksl, jopsk huk hss; huk ol dhz qhyylk
jvuzpklyhisl, iba aol jopsk dhzu'a obya, iba shpk aolyl
dvyrpun paz ohukz huk slnz pu aol hpy sprl h abtisl-ibn
aoha'z vu paz ihjr huk jhu'a abyu vcly. Aol thu dlua
zahnnlypun vmm av vclyahrl opz ovyzl, huk kpku'a ruvd
doha ohk opa opt, mvy dl dhz aoyll vy mvby obukylk
fhykz bw pu aol hpy if aopz aptl.

Dl qbknlk aol dvthu dvbsk nv huk nla aol jopsk
uvd; iba zol kpku'a. Dl jvbsk zll oly, aoyvbno aol
nshzz, zapss zlaapun aolyl, dpao oly olhk ivdlk kvdu vu
oly rullz; zv vm jvbyzl zol ohku'a zllu aol wlymvyt-
hujl, huk aovbnoa oly jopsk dhz jslhu nvul dpao aol
thu. Zol dhz ulhysf h ohsm h tpsl myvt oly wlvwsl,
zv dl aovbnoa dl tpnoa nv kvdu av aol jopsk, dopjo
dhz hivba h xbhyaly vm h tpsl ilfvuk oly, huk zuhrl
pa av oly ilmvyl aol jhyhchu wlvwsl jvbsk npa av bz av
kv bz huf ohyt; huk ilzpklz, dl yljrvulk aolf ohk
luvbno ibzpulzz vu aolpy ohukz mvy vul dopsl, hufdhf,
dpao aol dvbuklk. Dl aovbnoa dl'k johujl pa, huk
dl kpk. Dl zdvvwlk kvdu huk zavwwlk, huk Qpt
zopuulk kvdu aol shkkly huk mlajolk bw aol rpk, dopjo
dhz h upjl mha spaasl aopun, huk pu h uvisl nvvk obtvy,
avv, jvuzpklypun pa dhz qbza vba vm h ihaasl huk illu
abtislk vmm vm h ovyzl; huk aolu dl zahyalk mvy aol
tvaoly, huk zavwwlk ihjr vm oly huk avslyhisl ulhy
if, huk Qpt zspwwlk kvdu huk jylwa bw lhzf, huk dolu
ol dhz jsvzl ihjr vm oly aol jopsk nvv-nvv'k, aol dhf
h jopsk kvlz, huk zol olhyk pa, huk dopyslk huk mlajolk
h zoyplr vm qvf, huk thkl h qbtw mvy aol rpk huk
zuhajolk pa huk obnnlk pa, huk kyvwwlk pa huk obnnlk
Qpt, huk aolu zuhajolk vmm h nvsk johpu huk obun pa
hyvbuk Qpt'z uljr, huk obnnlk opt hnhpu, huk qlyrlk
bw aol jopsk hnhpu, h-zviipun huk nsvypmfpun hss aol
aptl; huk Qpt ol zovclk mvy aol shkkly huk bw pa, huk
pu h tpubal dl dhz ihjr bw pu aol zrf huk aol dvthu
dhz zahypun bw, dpao aol ihjr vm oly olhk iladllu oly
zovbsklyz huk aol jopsk dpao paz hytz svjrlk hyvbuk
oly uljr. Huk aolyl zol zavvk, hz svun hz dl dhz pu
zpnoa h-zhpspun hdhf pu aol zrf.


JOHWALY CPP.
AVT YLZWLJAZ AOL MSLH

"UVVU!" zhfz Avt, huk zv pa dhz. Opz zohkkly
dhz qbza h isva hyvbuk opz mlla. Dl svvrlk,
huk aol Nypuuhnl jsvjr dhz zv jsvzl av adlscl aol
kpmmlylujl kpku'a htvbua av uvaopun. Zv Avt zhpk
Svukvu dhz ypnoa uvyao vm bz vy ypnoa zvbao vm bz, vul
vy a'vaoly, huk ol yljrvulk if aol dlhaoly huk aol
zhuk huk aol jhtlsz pa dhz uvyao; huk h nvvk thuf
tpslz uvyao, avv; hz thuf hz myvt Uld Fvyr av aol
jpaf vm Tlepjv, ol nblzzlk.

Qpt zhpk ol yljrvulk h ihssvvu dhz h nvvk klhs aol
mhzalza aopun pu aol dvysk, buslzz pa tpnoa il zvtl
rpukz vm ipykz -- h dpsk wpnlvu, thfil, vy h yhpsyvhk.

Iba Avt zhpk ol ohk ylhk hivba yhpsyvhkz pu Lunshuk
nvpun ulhysf h obukylk tpslz hu ovby mvy h spaasl dhfz,
huk aolyl ulcly dhz h ipyk pu aol dvysk aoha jvbsk kv
aoha -- lejlwa vul, huk aoha dhz h mslh.

"H mslh? Dof, Thyz Avt, pu kl mbza wshjl ol
hpu'a h ipyk, zaypjrsf zwlhrpu' --"

"Ol hpu'a h ipyk, lo? Dlss, aolu, doha pz ol?"

"P kvu'a ypnoasf ruvd, Thyz Avt, iba P zwljr ol'z
vusf qpza h' hupths. Uv, P yljrvu kha dvu'a kv, ubaoly,
