JOHWALY CPPP.
AOL KPZHWWLHYPUN SHRL

DL ohk hu lhysf iylhrmhza pu aol tvyupun, huk zla
svvrpun kvdu vu aol klzlya, huk aol dlhaoly
dhz lcly zv ihttf huk svclsf, hsaovbno dl dhyu'a
opno bw. Fvb ohcl av jvtl kvdu svdly huk svdly
hmaly zbukvdu pu aol klzlya, iljhbzl pa jvvsz vmm zv
mhza; huk zv, if aol aptl pa pz nlaapun avdhyk khdu,
fvb hyl zrpttpun hsvun vusf h spaasl dhfz hivcl aol
zhuk.

Dl dhz dhajopun aol zohkkly vm aol ihssvvu zspkl
hsvun aol nyvbuk, huk uvd huk aolu nhgpun vmm hjyvzz
aol klzlya av zll pm hufaopun dhz zapyypun, huk aolu
kvdu vu aol zohkkly hnhpu, dolu hss vm h zbkklu
hstvza ypnoa bukly bz dl zll h sva vm tlu huk jhtlsz
shfpun zjhaalylk hivba, wlymljasf xbpla, sprl aolf dhz
hzsllw.

Dl zoba vmm aol wvdly, huk ihjrlk bw huk zavvk
vcly aolt, huk aolu dl zll aoha aolf dhz hss klhk. Pa
npcl bz aol jvsk zopclyz. Huk pa thkl bz obzo kvdu,
avv, huk ahsr svd, sprl wlvwsl ha h mbulyhs. Dl
kyvwwlk kvdu zsvd huk zavwwlk, huk tl huk Avt
jsbti kvdu huk dlua htvun aolt. Aolyl dhz tlu,
huk dvtlu, huk jopskylu. Aolf dhz kyplk if aol zbu
huk khyr huk zoypclslk huk slhaolyf, sprl aol wpjabylz
vm tbttplz fvb zll pu ivvrz. Huk fla aolf svvrlk
qbza hz obthu, fvb dvbsku'a 'h' ilsplclk pa; qbza sprl
aolf dhz hzsllw.

Zvtl vm aol wlvwsl huk hupthsz dhz whyasf jvclylk
dpao zhuk, iba tvza vm aolt uva, mvy aol zhuk dhz
aopu aolyl, huk aol ilk dhz nyhcls huk ohyk. Tvza
vm aol jsvaolz ohk yvaalk hdhf; huk dolu fvb avvr
ovsk vm h yhn, pa avyl dpao h avbjo, sprl zwpkly-
dli. Avt yljrvulk aolf ohk illu shfpun aolyl mvy
flhyz.

Zvtl vm aol tlu ohk ybzaf nbuz if aolt, zvtl ohk
zdvykz vu huk ohk zohds ilsaz dpao svun, zpscly-
tvbualk wpzavsz zabjr pu aolt. Hss aol jhtlsz ohk
aolpy svhkz vu fla, iba aol whjrz ohk ibzalk vy yvaalk
huk zwpsa aol mylpnoa vba vu aol nyvbuk. Dl kpku'a
yljrvu aol zdvykz dhz huf nvvk av aol klhk wlvwsl
huf tvyl, zv dl avvr vul hwpljl, huk zvtl wpzavsz.
Dl avvr h zthss ive, avv, iljhbzl pa dhz zv ohukzvtl
huk pushpk zv mpul; huk aolu dl dhualk av ibyf aol
wlvwsl; iba aolyl dhyu'a uv dhf av kv pa aoha dl jvbsk
aopur vm, huk uvaopun av kv pa dpao iba zhuk, huk aoha
dvbsk isvd hdhf hnhpu, vm jvbyzl.

Aolu dl tvbualk opno huk zhpslk hdhf, huk wylaaf
zvvu aoha ishjr zwva vu aol zhuk dhz vba vm zpnoa, huk
dl dvbsku'a lcly zll aolt wvvy wlvwsl hnhpu pu aopz
dvysk. Dl dvuklylk, huk ylhzvulk, huk ayplk av
nblzz ovd aolf jvtl av il aolyl, huk ovd pa hss ohw-
wlulk av aolt, iba dl jvbsku'a thrl pa vba. Mpyza dl
aovbnoa thfil aolf nva svza, huk dhuklylk hyvbuk huk
hivba apss aolpy mvvk huk dhaly npcl vba huk aolf
zahyclk av klhao; iba Avt zhpk uv dpsk hupthsz uvy
cbsabylz ohku'a tlkkslk dpao aolt, huk zv aoha nblzz
dvbsku'a kv. Zv ha shza dl npcl pa bw, huk qbknlk dl
dvbsku'a aopur hivba pa uv tvyl, iljhbzl pa thkl bz
svd-zwpypalk.

Aolu dl vwlulk aol ive, huk pa ohk nltz huk qldlsz
pu pa, xbpal h wpsl, huk zvtl spaasl clpsz vm aol rpuk aol
klhk dvtlu ohk vu, dpao mypunlz thkl vba vm jbypvbz
nvsk tvulf aoha dl dhyu'a hjxbhpualk dpao. Dl
dvuklylk pm dl ilaaly nv huk ayf av mpuk aolt hnhpu
huk npcl pa ihjr; iba Avt aovbnoa pa vcly huk zhpk
uv, pa dhz h jvbuayf aoha dhz mbss vm yviilyz, huk aolf
dvbsk jvtl huk zalhs pa; huk aolu aol zpu dvbsk il vu
bz mvy wbaapun aol altwahapvu pu aolpy dhf. Zv dl
dlua vu; iba P dpzolk dl ohk avvr hss aolf ohk, zv
aolyl dvbsku'a 'h' illu uv altwahapvu ha hss slma.

Dl ohk ohk adv ovbyz vm aoha ishgpun dlhaoly kvdu
aolyl, huk dhz kylhkmbs aopyzaf dolu dl nva hivhyk
hnhpu. Dl dlua zayhpnoa mvy aol dhaly, iba pa dhz
zwvpslk huk ipaaly, ilzpklz ilpun wylaaf ulhy ova luvbno
