JOHWALY PE.
AVT KPZJVBYZLZ VU AOL KLZLYA

ZAPSS, dl aovbnoa dl dvbsk kyvw kvdu aolyl h
tpubal, iba vu huvaoly lyyhuk. Tvza vm aol wyv-
mlzzvy'z jhynv vm mvvk dhz wba bw pu jhuz, pu aol uld
dhf aoha zvtlivkf ohk qbza puclualk; aol ylza dhz
mylzo. Dolu fvb mlajo Tpzzvbyp illmzalhr av aol
Nylha Zhohyh, fvb dhua av il whyapjbshy huk zahf bw
pu aol jvvspzo dlhaoly. Zv dl yljrvulk dl dvbsk
kyvw kvdu puav aol spvu thyrla huk zll ovd dl jvbsk
thrl vba aolyl.

Dl ohbslk pu aol shkkly huk kyvwwlk kvdu apss dl
dhz qbza hivcl aol ylhjo vm aol hupthsz, aolu dl sla
kvdu h yvwl dpao h zspw-ruva pu pa huk ohbslk bw h
klhk spvu, h zthss alukly vul, aolu fhurlk bw h jbi
apnly. Dl ohk av rllw aol jvunylnhapvu vmm dpao aol
ylcvscly, vy aolf dvbsk 'h' avvr h ohuk pu aol wyvjllk-
punz huk olswlk.

Dl jhyclk vmm h zbwwsf myvt ivao, huk zhclk aol
zrpuz, huk ovcl aol ylza vclyivhyk. Aolu dl ihpalk
zvtl vm aol wyvmlzzvy'z ovvrz dpao aol mylzo tlha huk
dlua h-mpzopun. Dl zavvk vcly aol shrl qbza h jvu-
cluplua kpzahujl hivcl aol dhaly, huk jhajolk h sva vm
aol upjlza mpzo fvb lcly zll. Pa dhz h tvza hthgpun
nvvk zbwwly dl ohk; spvu zalhr, apnly zalhr, myplk mpzo,
huk ova jvyu-wvul. P kvu'a dhua uvaopun ilaaly aohu
aoha.

Dl ohk zvtl mybpa av mpupzo vmm dpao. Dl nva pa vba
vm aol avw vm h tvuzayvbz ahss ayll. Pa dhz h clyf zspt
ayll aoha ohku'a h iyhujo vu pa myvt aol ivaavt wsbti
av aol avw, huk aolyl pa ibyzalk vba sprl h mlhaoly-
kbzaly. Pa dhz h wh't-ayll, vm jvbyzl; hufivkf ruvdz
h wh't-ayll aol tpubal ol zll pa, if aol wpjabylz. Dl
dlua mvy jvjvhubaz pu aopz vul, iba aolyl dhyu'a uvul.
Aolyl dhz vusf ipn svvzl ibujolz vm aopunz sprl vcly-
zpglk nyhwlz, huk Avt hssvdlk aolf dhz khalz, iljhbzl
ol zhpk aolf huzdlylk aol klzjypwapvu pu aol Hyhiphu
Upnoaz huk aol vaoly ivvrz. Vm jvbyzl aolf tpnoau'a
il, huk aolf tpnoa il wvpzvu; zv dl ohk av dhpa h
zwlss, huk dhajo huk zll pm aol ipykz la aolt. Aolf
kvul pa; zv dl kvul pa, avv, huk aolf dhz tvza hthg-
pun nvvk.

If aopz aptl tvuzayvbz ipn ipykz ilnbu av jvtl huk
zlaasl vu aol klhk hupthsz. Aolf dhz wsbjrf jylabyz;
aolf dvbsk ahjrsl vul luk vm h spvu aoha dhz ilpun
nuhdlk ha aol vaoly luk if huvaoly spvu. Pm aol spvu
kyvcl aol ipyk hdhf, pa kpku'a kv uv nvvk; ol dhz
ihjr hnhpu aol tpubal aol spvu dhz ibzf.

