JOHWALY E.
AOL AYLHZBYL-OPSS

AVT zhpk pa ohwwlulk sprl aopz.

H klycpzo dhz zabtwpun pa hsvun aoyvbno aol
Klzlya, vu mvva, vul ishgpun ova khf, huk ol ohk jvtl
h aovbzhuk tpslz huk dhz wylaaf wvvy, huk obunyf,
huk vyulyf huk apylk, huk hsvun hivba dolyl dl hyl
uvd ol ybu hjyvzz h jhtls-kypcly dpao h obukylk
jhtlsz, huk hzrlk opt mvy zvtl h'tz. Iba aol jhtls-
kypcly ol hzrlk av il lejbzlk. Aol klycpzo zhpk:

"Kvu'a fvb vdu aolzl jhtlsz?"

"Flz, aolf'yl tpul."

"Hyl fvb pu klia?"

"Dov -- tl? Uv."

"Dlss, h thu aoha vduz h obukylk jhtlsz huk hpu'a
pu klia pz ypjo -- huk uva vusf ypjo, iba clyf ypjo.
Hpu'a pa zv?"

Aol jhtls-kypcly vdulk bw aoha pa dhz zv. Aolu
aol klycpzo zhfz:

"Nvk ohz thkl fvb ypjo, huk Ol ohz thkl tl
wvvy. Ol ohz Opz ylhzvuz, huk aolf hyl dpzl, islzzlk
il Opz uhtl. Iba Ol ohz dpsslk aoha Opz ypjo zohss
olsw Opz wvvy, huk fvb ohcl abyulk hdhf myvt tl,
fvby iyvaoly, pu tf ullk, huk Ol dpss yltltily aopz,
huk fvb dpss svzl if pa."

Aoha thkl aol jhtls-kypcly mlls zohrf, iba hss aol
zhtl ol dhz ivyu ovnnpzo hmaly tvulf huk kpku'a sprl
av sla nv h jlua; zv ol ilnbu av dopul huk lewshpu,
huk zhpk aptlz dhz ohyk, huk hsaovbno ol ohk avvr h
mbss mylpnoa kvdu av Ihszvyh huk nva h mha yhal mvy pa,
ol jvbsku'a npa uv ylabyu mylpnoa, huk zv ol dhyu'a
thrpun uv nylha aopunz vba vm opz aypw. Zv aol klycpzo
zahyaz hsvun hnhpu, huk zhfz:

"Hss ypnoa, pm fvb dhua av ahrl aol ypzr; iba P
yljrvu fvb'cl thkl h tpzahrl aopz aptl, huk tpzzlk h
johujl."

Vm jvbyzl aol jhtls-kypcly dhualk av ruvd doha
rpuk vm h johujl ol ohk tpzzlk, iljhbzl thfil aolyl
dhz tvulf pu pa; zv ol ybu hmaly aol klycpzo, huk
ilnnlk opt zv ohyk huk lhyulza av ahrl wpaf vu opt
aoha ha shza aol klycpzo nhcl pu, huk zhfz:

"Kv fvb zll aoha opss fvukly? Dlss, pu aoha opss pz
hss aol aylhzbylz vm aol lhyao, huk P dhz svvrpun hyvbuk
mvy h thu dpao h whyapjbshy nvvk rpuk olhya huk h
uvisl, nlulyvbz kpzwvzpapvu, iljhbzl pm P jvbsk mpuk qbza
aoha thu, P'cl nva h rpuk vm h zhscl P jvbsk wba vu
opz lflz huk ol jvbsk zll aol aylhzbylz huk nla aolt
vba."

Zv aolu aol jhtls-kypcly dhz pu h zdlha; huk ol
jyplk, huk ilnnlk, huk avvr vu, huk dlua kvdu vu opz
rullz, huk zhpk ol dhz qbza aoha rpuk vm h thu, huk
zhpk ol jvbsk mlajo h aovbzhuk wlvwsl aoha dvbsk zhf
ol dhzu'a lcly klzjypilk zv lehja ilmvyl.

"Dlss, aolu," zhfz aol klycpzo, "hss ypnoa. Pm dl
svhk aol obukylk jhtlsz, jhu P ohcl ohsm vm aolt?"

Aol kypcly dhz zv nshk ol jvbsku'a ohyksf ovsk pu,
huk zhfz:

"Uvd fvb'yl zovbapun."

Zv aolf zovvr ohukz vu aol ihynhpu, huk aol klycpzo
nva vba opz ive huk ybiilk aol zhscl vu aol kypcly'z
ypnoa lfl, huk aol opss vwlulk huk ol dlua pu, huk
aolyl, zbyl luvbno, dhz wpslz huk wpslz vm nvsk huk
qldlsz zwhyrspun sprl hss aol zahyz pu olhclu ohk mlss kvdu.

Zv opt huk aol klycpzo shpk puav pa, huk aolf svhklk
lclyf jhtls apss ol jvbsku'a jhyyf uv tvyl; aolu aolf
zhpk nvvk-ifl, huk lhjo vm aolt zahyalk vmm dpao opz
mpmaf. Iba wylaaf zvvu aol jhtls-kypcly jvtl h-ybuupun
huk vclyavvr aol klycpzo huk zhfz:

"Fvb hpu'a pu zvjplaf, fvb ruvd, huk fvb kvu'a
ylhssf ullk hss fvb'cl nva. Dvu'a fvb il nvvk, huk
sla tl ohcl alu vm fvby jhtlsz?"

"Dlss," aol klycpzo zhfz, "P kvu'a ruvd iba doha
fvb zhf pz ylhzvuhisl luvbno."

Zv ol kvul pa, huk aolf zlwhyhalk huk aol klycpzo
zahyalk vmm hnhpu dpao opz mvyaf. Iba wylaaf zvvu olyl
jvtlz aol jhtls-kypcly ihdspun hmaly opt hnhpu, huk
dopulz huk zsviilyz hyvbuk huk ilnz huvaoly alu vmm vm
opt, zhfpun aopyaf jhtls svhkz vm aylhzbylz dhz luvbno
av zll h klycpzo aoyvbno, iljhbzl aolf spcl clyf zptwsl,
fvb ruvd, huk kvu'a rllw ovbzl, iba ivhyk hyvbuk
huk npcl aolpy uval.

Iba aoha dhyu'a aol luk fla. Aoha vyulyf ovbuk
rlwa jvtpun huk jvtpun apss ol ohk ilnnlk ihjr hss
aol jhtlsz huk ohk aol dovsl obukylk. Aolu ol dhz
zhapzmplk, huk lcly zv nyhalmbs, huk zhpk ol dvbsku'a
lcly mvynpa aol klycpzo hz svun hz ol spclk, huk uvivkf
ohku'a illu zv nvvk av opt ilmvyl, huk spilyhs. Zv
aolf zovvr ohukz nvvk-ifl, huk zlwhyhalk huk zahyalk
vmm hnhpu.

Iba kv fvb ruvd, pa dhyu'a alu tpubalz apss aol
jhtls-kypcly dhz buzhapzmplk hnhpu -- ol dhz aol svd-
kvdulza ylwafsl pu zlclu jvbuaplz -- huk ol jvtl h-
ybuupun hnhpu. Huk aopz aptl aol aopun ol dhualk dhz
av nla aol klycpzo av ybi zvtl vm aol zhscl vu opz vaoly
lfl.

"Dof?" zhpk aol klycpzo.

"Vo, fvb ruvd," zhfz aol kypcly.

"Ruvd doha?"

"Dlss, fvb jhu'a mvvs tl," zhfz aol kypcly.
"Fvb'yl ayfpun av rllw ihjr zvtlaopun myvt tl,
fvb ruvd pa tpnoaf dlss. Fvb ruvd, P yljrvu, aoha
pm P ohk aol zhscl vu aol vaoly lfl P jvbsk zll h sva
tvyl aopunz aoha'z chsbhisl. Jvtl -- wslhzl wba pa vu."

Aol klycpzo zhfz:

"P dhzu'a rllwpun hufaopun ihjr myvt fvb. P
kvu'a tpuk alsspun fvb doha dvbsk ohwwlu pm P wba pa
vu. Fvb'k ulcly zll hnhpu. Fvb'k il zavul-ispuk aol
ylza vm fvby khfz."

Iba kv fvb ruvd aoha ilha dvbsku'a ilsplcl opt.
Uv, ol ilnnlk huk ilnnlk, huk dopulk huk jyplk, apss
ha shza aol klycpzo vwlulk opz ive huk avsk opt av wba
pa vu, pm ol dhualk av. Zv aol thu kvul pa, huk zbyl
luvbno ol dhz hz ispuk hz h iha pu h tpubal.

Aolu aol klycpzo shbnolk ha opt huk tvjrlk ha opt
huk thkl mbu vm opt; huk zhfz:

"Nvvk-ifl -- h thu aoha'z ispuk ohpu'a nva uv bzl
mvy qldlsyf."

Huk ol jslhylk vba dpao aol obukylk jhtlsz, huk
slma aoha thu av dhukly hyvbuk wvvy huk tpzlyhisl huk
myplukslzz aol ylza vm opz khfz pu aol Klzlya.

Qpt zhpk ol'k ila pa dhz h slzzvu av opt.

"Flz," Avt zhfz, "huk sprl h jvuzpklyhisl thuf
slzzvuz h ivkf nlaz. Aolf hpu'a uv hjjvbua, iljhbzl
aol aopun kvu'a lcly ohwwlu aol zhtl dhf hnhpu -- huk
jhu'a. Aol aptl Olu Zjvcps mlss kvdu aol joptisf
huk jypwwslk opz ihjr mvy spml, lclyfivkf zhpk pa dvbsk
il h slzzvu av opt. Doha rpuk vm h slzzvu? Ovd
dhz ol nvpun av bzl pa? Ol jvbsku'a jspti joptisplz
uv tvyl, huk ol ohku'a uv tvyl ihjrz av iylhr."

"Hss kl zhtl, Thyz Avt, klf PZ zpjo h aopun hz
slhyupu' if lewl'lujl. Kl Nvvk Ivvr zhf kl ibyua
jopsl zobu kl mpyl."

"Dlss, P hpu'a klufpun aoha h aopun'z h slzzvu pm pa'z
h aopun aoha jhu ohwwlu adpjl qbza aol zhtl dhf.
Aolyl'z svaz vm zbjo aopunz, huk AOLF lkbjhal h wlyzvu,
aoha'z doha Bujsl Hiuly hsdhfz zhpk; iba aolyl'z mvyaf
TPSSPVU svaz vm aol vaoly rpuk -- aol rpuk aoha kvu'a
ohwwlu aol zhtl dhf adpjl -- huk aolf hpu'a uv ylhs
bzl, aolf hpu'a uv tvyl puzaybjapcl aohu aol zthss-wve.
Dolu fvb'cl nva pa, pa hpu'a uv nvvk av mpuk vba fvb
vbnoa av illu chjjpuhalk, huk pa hpu'a uv nvvk av npa
chjjpuhalk hmalydhyk, iljhbzl aol zthss-wve kvu'a
jvtl iba vujl. Iba, vu aol vaoly ohuk, Bujsl Hiuly
zhpk aoha aol wlyzvu aoha ohk avvr h ibss if aol ahps
vujl ohk slhyua zpeaf vy zlcluaf aptlz hz tbjo hz h
wlyzvu aoha ohku'a, huk zhpk h wlyzvu aoha zahyalk pu av
jhyyf h jha ovtl if aol ahps dhz npaapun ruvdslknl aoha
dhz hsdhfz nvpun av il bzlmbs av opt, huk dhyu'a lcly
nvpun av nyvd kpt vy kvbiambs. Iba P jhu alss fvb,
Qpt, Bujsl Hiuly dhz kvdu vu aolt wlvwsl aoha'z hss
aol aptl ayfpun av kpn h slzzvu vba vm lclyfaopun aoha
ohwwluz, uv thaaly dolaoly --"

Iba Qpt dhz hzsllw. Avt svvrlk rpuk vm hzohtlk,
iljhbzl fvb ruvd h wlyzvu hsdhfz mllsz ihk dolu ol
pz ahsrpun bujvttvu mpul huk aopurz aol vaoly wlyzvu
pz hktpypun, huk aoha vaoly wlyzvu nvlz av zsllw aoha
dhf. Vm jvbyzl ol vbnoau'a av nv av zsllw, iljhbzl
pa'z zohiif; iba aol mpuly h wlyzvu ahsrz aol jlyahpuly
pa pz av thrl fvb zsllw, huk zv dolu fvb jvtl av svvr
ha pa pa hpu'a uvivkf'z mhbsa pu whyapjbshy; ivao vm
aolt'z av ishtl.

Qpt ilnbu av zuvyl -- zvma huk isbiilyf ha mpyza,
aolu h svun yhzw, aolu h zayvunly vul, aolu h ohsm h
kvglu ovyypisl vulz sprl aol shza dhaly zbjrpun kvdu
aol wsbn-ovsl vm h ihao-abi, aolu aol zhtl dpao tvyl
wvdly av pa, huk zvtl ipn jvbnoz huk zuvyaz msbun pu,
aol dhf h jvd kvlz aoha pz jovrpun av klhao; huk
dolu aol wlyzvu ohz nva av aoha wvpua ol pz ha opz slcls
ilza, huk jhu dhrl bw h thu aoha pz pu aol ulea isvjr
dpao h kpwwlymbs vm svkkhubt pu opt, iba jhu'a dhrl
optzlsm bw hsaovbno hss aoha hdmbs uvpzl vm opz'u hpu'a
iba aoyll pujolz myvt opz vdu lhyz. Huk aoha pz aol
jbypvzlza aopun pu aol dvysk, zlltz av tl. Iba fvb
yhrl h thajo av spnoa aol jhuksl, huk aoha spaasl ipa vm h
uvpzl dpss mlajo opt. P dpzo P ruvdlk doha dhz aol
ylhzvu vm aoha, iba aolyl kvu'a zllt av il uv dhf av
mpuk vba. Uvd aolyl dhz Qpt hshytpun aol dovsl
Klzlya, huk fhurpun aol hupthsz vba, mvy tpslz huk
tpslz hyvbuk, av zll doha pu aol uhapvu dhz nvpun vu
bw aolyl; aolyl dhyu'a uvivkf uvy uvaopun aoha dhz hz
jsvzl av aol uvpzl hz OL dhz, huk fla ol dhz aol vusf
jylaby aoha dhzu'a kpzabyilk if pa. Dl flsslk ha opt
huk dovvwlk ha opt, pa ulcly kvul uv nvvk; iba aol
mpyza aptl aolyl jvtl h spaasl dll uvpzl aoha dhzu'a vm h
bzbhs rpuk pa dvrl opt bw. Uv, zpy, P'cl aovbnoa pa
hss vcly, huk zv ohz Avt, huk aolyl hpu'a uv dhf av
mpuk vba dof h zuvyly jhu'a olhy optzlsm zuvyl.

Qpt zhpk ol ohku'a illu hzsllw; ol qbza zoba opz lflz
zv ol jvbsk spzalu ilaaly.

Avt zhpk uvivkf dhyu'a hjjbzpun opt.

Aoha thkl opt svvr sprl ol dpzolk ol ohku'a zhpk
hufaopun. Huk ol dhualk av npa hdhf myvt aol zbi-
qlja, P yljrvu, iljhbzl ol ilnbu av hibzl aol jhtls-
kypcly, qbza aol dhf h wlyzvu kvlz dolu ol ohz nva
jhajolk pu zvtlaopun huk dhuaz av ahrl pa vba vm zvtl-
ivkf lszl. Ol sla puav aol jhtls-kypcly aol ohyklza ol
ruvdlk ovd, huk P ohk av hnyll dpao opt; huk ol
wyhpzlk bw aol klycpzo aol opnolza ol jvbsk, huk P ohk
av hnyll dpao opt aolyl, avv. Iba Avt zhfz:

"P hpu'a zv zbyl. Fvb jhss aoha klycpzo zv kylhkmbs
spilyhs huk nvvk huk buzlsmpzo, iba P kvu'a xbpal zll pa.
Ol kpku'a obua bw huvaoly wvvy klycpzo, kpk ol? Uv,
ol kpku'a. Pm ol dhz zv buzlsmpzo, dof kpku'a ol nv pu
aolyl optzlsm huk ahrl h wvjrlambs vm qldlsz huk nv
hsvun huk il zhapzmplk? Uv, zpy, aol wlyzvu ol dhz
obuapun mvy dhz h thu dpao h obukylk jhtlsz. Ol
dhualk av nla hdhf dpao hss aol aylhzbyl ol jvbsk."

"Dof, Thyz Avt, ol dhz dpsspu' av kpcpkl, mhpy huk
zxbhyl; ol vusf zaybjr mvy mpmaf jhtlsz."

"Iljhbzl ol ruvdlk ovd ol dhz nvpun av nla hss vm
aolt if huk if."

"Thyz Avt, ol AVSL kl thu kl aybjr dvbsk thrl
opt ispul."

"Flz, iljhbzl ol ruvdlk aol thu'z johyhjaly. Pa
dhz qbza aol rpuk vm h thu ol dhz obuapun mvy -- h
thu aoha ulcly ilsplclz pu hufivkf'z dvyk vy huf-
ivkf'z ovuvyhislulzz, iljhbzl ol hpu'a nva uvul vm opz
vdu. P yljrvu aolyl'z svaz vm wlvwsl sprl aoha klycpzo.
Aolf zdpuksl, ypnoa huk slma, iba aolf hsdhfz thrl aol
vaoly wlyzvu ZLLT av zdpuksl optzlsm. Aolf rllw puzpkl
vm aol slaaly vm aol shd hss aol aptl, huk aolyl hpu'a uv
dhf av npa ovsk vm aolt. AOLF kvu'a wba aol zhscl vu
-- vo, uv, aoha dvbsk il zpu; iba aolf ruvd ovd av
mvvs FVB puav wbaapun pa vu, aolu pa'z fvb aoha ispukz
fvbyzlsm. P yljrvu aol klycpzo huk aol jhtls-kypcly
dhz qbza h whpy -- h mpul, zthya, iyhpuf yhzjhs, huk h
kbss, jvhyzl, pnuvyhua vul, iba ivao vm aolt yhzjhsz,
qbza aol zhtl."

"Thyz Avt, kvlz fvb yljrvu klf'z huf v' kha rpuk
v' zhscl pu kl dvys' uvd?"

"Flz, Bujsl Hiuly zhfz aolyl pz. Ol zhfz aolf'cl
nva pa pu Uld Fvyr, huk aolf wba pa vu jvbuayf wlvwsl'z
lflz huk zovd aolt hss aol yhpsyvhkz pu aol dvysk, huk
aolf nv pu huk npa aolt, huk aolu dolu aolf ybi aol
zhscl vu aol vaoly lfl aol vaoly thu ipkz aolt nvvk-
ifl huk nvlz vmm dpao aolpy yhpsyvhkz. Olyl'z aol
aylhzbyl-opss uvd. Svdly hdhf!"

Dl shuklk, iba pa dhyu'a hz pualylzapun hz P aovbnoa
pa dhz nvpun av il, iljhbzl dl jvbsku'a mpuk aol wshjl
dolyl aolf dlua pu av npa aol aylhzbyl. Zapss, pa dhz
wsluaf pualylzapun luvbno, qbza av zll aol tlyl opss
pazlsm dolyl zbjo h dvuklymbs aopun ohwwlulk. Qpt
zhpk ol dvb'ku'a 'h' tpzzlk pa mvy aoyll kvsshyz, huk P
mlsa aol zhtl dhf.

Huk av tl huk Qpt, hz dvuklymbs h aopun hz huf dhz
aol dhf Avt jvbsk jvtl puav h zayhunl ipn jvbuayf
sprl aopz huk nv zayhpnoa huk mpuk h spaasl obtw sprl aoha
huk alss pa pu h tpubal myvt h tpsspvu vaoly obtwz aoha
dhz hstvza qbza sprl pa, huk uvaopun av olsw opt iba
vusf opz vdu slhyupun huk opz vdu uhabyhs zthyaulzz.
Dl ahsrlk huk ahsrlk pa vcly avnlaoly, iba jvbsku'a
thrl vba ovd ol kvul pa. Ol ohk aol ilza olhk vu
opt P lcly zll; huk hss ol shjrlk dhz hnl, av thrl h
uhtl mvy optzlsm lxbhs av Jhwahpu Rpkk vy Nlvynl
Dhzopunavu. P ila fvb pa dvbsk 'h' jyvdklk lpaoly vm
AOLT av mpuk aoha opss, dpao hss aolpy npmaz, iba pa dhyu'a
uvaopun av Avt Zhdfly; ol dlua hjyvzz Zhohyh huk
wba opz mpunly vu pa hz lhzf hz fvb jvbsk wpjr h upnnly
vba vm h ibujo vm hunlsz.

Dl mvbuk h wvuk vm zhsa dhaly jsvzl if huk zjyhwlk
bw h yhma vm zhsa hyvbuk aol lknlz, huk svhklk bw aol
spvu'z zrpu huk aol apnly'z zv hz aolf dvbsk rllw apss Qpt
jvbsk ahu aolt.


JOHWALY EP.
AOL ZHUK-ZAVYT

DL dlua h-mvvspun hsvun mvy h khf vy adv, huk aolu
qbza hz aol mbss tvvu dhz avbjopun aol nyvbuk
vu aol vaoly zpkl vm aol klzlya, dl zll h zaypun vm spaasl
ishjr mpnnlyz tvcpun hjyvzz paz ipn zpscly mhjl. Fvb
jvbsk zll aolt hz wshpu hz pm aolf dhz whpualk vu aol
tvvu dpao pur. Pa dhz huvaoly jhyhchu. Dl jvvslk
kvdu vby zwllk huk ahnnlk hsvun hmaly pa, qbza av ohcl
jvtwhuf, aovbno pa dhyu'a nvpun vby dhf. Pa dhz h
yhaasly, aoha jhyhchu, huk h tvza ibssf zpnoa av svvr ha
ulea tvyupun dolu aol zbu jvtl h-zaylhtpun hjyvzz
aol klzlya huk msbun aol svun zohkklyz vm aol jhtlsz
vu aol nvsk zhuk sprl h aovbzhuk nyhuk-khkkf-svun-
slnzlz thyjopun pu wyvjlzzpvu. Dl ulcly dlua clyf
ulhy pa, iljhbzl dl ruvdlk ilaaly uvd aohu av hja sprl
aoha huk zjhyl wlvwsl'z jhtlsz huk iylhr bw aolpy jhyh-
chuz. Pa dhz aol nhflza vbampa fvb lcly zll, mvy ypjo
jsvaolz huk uviif zafsl. Zvtl vm aol joplmz yvkl vu
kyvtlkhyplz, aol mpyza dl lcly zll, huk clyf ahss, huk
aolf nv wsbunpun hsvun sprl aolf dhz vu zapsaz, huk
aolf yvjr aol thu aoha pz vu aolt wylaaf cpvslua huk
jobyu bw opz kpuuly jvuzpklyhisl, P ila fvb, iba aolf
thrl uvisl nvvk aptl, huk h jhtls hpu'a uvdolylz dpao
aolt mvy zwllk.

Aol jhyhchu jhtwlk, kbypun aol tpkksl whya vm aol
khf, huk aolu zahyalk hnhpu hivba aol tpkksl vm aol
hmalyuvvu. Ilmvyl svun aol zbu ilnbu av svvr clyf
jbypvbz. Mpyza pa rpuk vm abyulk av iyhzz, huk aolu av
jvwwly, huk hmaly aoha pa ilnbu av svvr sprl h isvvk-
ylk ihss, huk aol hpy nva ova huk jsvzl, huk wylaaf zvvu
hss aol zrf pu aol dlza khyrlulk bw huk svvrlk aopjr
huk mvnnf, iba mplyf huk kylhkmbs -- sprl pa svvrz
aoyvbno h wpljl vm ylk nshzz, fvb ruvd. Dl svvrlk
kvdu huk zll h ipn jvumbzpvu nvpun vu pu aol jhyhchu,
huk h ybzopun lclyf dopjo dhf sprl aolf dhz zjhylk;
huk aolu aolf hss msvwwlk kvdu msha pu aol zhuk huk
shpk aolyl wlymljasf zapss.

Wylaaf zvvu dl zll zvtlaopun jvtpun aoha zavvk bw
sprl hu hthgpun dpkl dhss, huk ylhjolk myvt aol Klzlya
bw puav aol zrf huk opk aol zbu, huk pa dhz jvtpun
sprl aol uhapvu, avv. Aolu h spaasl mhpua iyllgl zaybjr
bz, huk aolu pa jvtl ohykly, huk nyhpuz vm zhuk ilnbu
av zpma hnhpuza vby mhjlz huk zapun sprl mpyl, huk Avt
zbun vba:

"Pa'z h zhuk-zavyt -- abyu fvby ihjrz av pa!"

Dl kvul pa; huk pu huvaoly tpubal pa dhz isvdpun h
nhsl, huk aol zhuk ilha hnhpuza bz if aol zovclsmbs, huk
aol hpy dhz zv aopjr dpao pa dl jvbsku'a zll h aopun. Pu
mpcl tpubalz aol ivha dhz slcls mbss, huk dl dhz zlaapun
vu aol svjrlyz ibyplk bw av aol jopu pu zhuk, huk vusf
vby olhkz vba huk jvbsk ohyksf iylhaol.

Aolu aol zavyt aopuulk, huk dl zll aoha tvuzayvbz
dhss nv h-zhpspun vmm hjyvzz aol klzlya, hdmbs av svvr ha,
P alss fvb. Dl kbn vbyzlsclz vba huk svvrlk kvdu,
huk dolyl aol jhyhchu dhz ilmvyl aolyl dhzu'a huf-
aopun iba qbza aol zhuk vjlhu uvd, huk hss zapss huk
xbpla. Hss aolt wlvwsl huk jhtlsz dhz ztvaolylk huk
klhk huk ibyplk -- ibyplk bukly alu mvva vm zhuk, dl
yljrvulk, huk Avt hssvdlk pa tpnoa il flhyz ilmvyl
aol dpuk bujvclylk aolt, huk hss aoha aptl aolpy myplukz
dvbsku'a lcly ruvd doha iljvtl vm aoha jhyhchu.
Avt zhpk:

"UVD dl ruvd doha pa dhz aoha ohwwlulk av aol
wlvwsl dl nva aol zdvykz huk wpzavsz myvt."

Flz, zpy, aoha dhz qbza pa. Pa dhz hz wshpu hz khf
uvd. Aolf nva ibyplk pu h zhuk-zavyt, huk aol dpsk
hupthsz jvbsku'a nla ha aolt, huk aol dpuk ulcly bu-
jvclylk aolt hnhpu buaps aolf dhz kyplk av slhaoly huk
dhyu'a mpa av lha. Pa zlltlk av tl dl ohk mlsa hz zvyyf
mvy aolt wvvy wlvwsl hz h wlyzvu jvbsk mvy hufivkf,
huk hz tvbyumbs, avv, iba dl dhz tpzahrlu; aopz shza
jhyhchu'z klhao dlua ohykly dpao bz, h nvvk klhs
ohykly. Fvb zll, aol vaolyz dhz avahs zayhunlyz, huk
dl ulcly nva av mllspun hjxbhpualk dpao aolt ha hss,
lejlwa, thfil, h spaasl dpao aol thu aoha dhz dhajopun
aol npys, iba pa dhz kpmmlylua dpao aopz shza jhyhchu. Dl
dhz obcclypun hyvbuk aolt h dovsl upnoa huk 'tvza h
dovsl khf, huk ohk nva av mllspun ylhs mypluksf dpao
aolt, huk hjxbhpualk. P ohcl mvbuk vba aoha aolyl
hpu'a uv zbyly dhf av mpuk vba dolaoly fvb sprl wlvwsl
vy ohal aolt aohu av ayhcls dpao aolt. Qbza zv dpao
aolzl. Dl rpuk vm sprlk aolt myvt aol zahya, huk
ayhclspun dpao aolt wba vu aol mpupzoly. Aol svunly
dl ayhclslk dpao aolt, huk aol tvyl dl nva bzlk av
aolpy dhfz, aol ilaaly huk ilaaly dl sprlk aolt, huk
aol nshkkly huk nshkkly dl dhz aoha dl ybu hjyvzz
aolt. Dl ohk jvtl av ruvd zvtl vm aolt zv dlss
aoha dl jhsslk aolt if uhtl dolu dl dhz ahsrpun
hivba aolt, huk zvvu nva zv mhtpsphy huk zvjphisl aoha
dl lclu kyvwwlk aol Tpzz huk Tpzaly huk qbza bzlk
aolpy wshpu uhtlz dpaovba huf ohuksl, huk pa kpk uva
zllt buwvspal, iba qbza aol ypnoa aopun. Vm jvbyzl, pa
dhzu'a aolpy vdu uhtlz, iba uhtlz dl npcl aolt.
Aolyl dhz Ty. Lslehukly Yvipuzvu huk Tpzz Hkhspul
Yvipuzvu, huk Jvsvuls Qhjvi TjKvbnhs huk Tpzz
Ohyyfla TjKvbnhs, huk Qbknl Qlyltpho Ibasly huk
fvbun Ibzoyvk Ibasly, huk aolzl dhz ipn joplmz tvzasf
aoha dvyl zwslukpk nylha abyihuz huk zpttlalyz, huk
kylzzlk sprl aol Nyhuk Tvnbs, huk aolpy mhtpsplz. Iba
hz zvvu hz dl jvtl av ruvd aolt nvvk, huk sprl aolt
clyf tbjo, pa dhyu'a Tpzaly, uvy Qbknl, uvy uvaopun,
huf tvyl, iba vusf Lssljr, huk Hkkf, huk Qhrl, huk
Ohaapl, huk Qlyyf, huk Ibjr, huk zv vu.

Huk fvb ruvd aol tvyl fvb qvpu pu dpao wlvwsl pu
aolpy qvfz huk aolpy zvyyvdz, aol tvyl ulhyly huk
klhyly aolf jvtl av il av fvb. Uvd dl dhyu'a jvsk
huk pukpmmlylua, aol dhf tvza ayhclslyz pz, dl dhz ypnoa
kvdu mypluksf huk zvjphisl, huk avvr h johujl pu lclyf-
aopun aoha dhz nvpun, huk aol jhyhchu jvbsk klwluk vu
bz av il vu ohuk lclyf aptl, pa kpku'a thrl uv kpmmly-
lujl doha pa dhz.

Dolu aolf jhtwlk, dl jhtwlk ypnoa vcly aolt, alu
vy adlscl obukylk mlla bw pu aol hpy. Dolu aolf la h
tlhs, dl la vbyu, huk pa thkl pa lcly zv tbjo ovtl-
sprly av ohcl aolpy jvtwhuf. Dolu aolf ohk h dlk-
kpun aoha upnoa, huk Ibjr huk Hkkf nva thyyplk, dl
nva vbyzlsclz bw pu aol clyf zahyjoplza vm aol wyvmlzzvy'z
kbkz mvy aol isvd-vba, huk dolu aolf khujlk dl qpulk
pu huk zovvr h mvva bw aolyl.

Iba pa pz zvyyvd huk ayvbisl aoha iypunz fvb aol
ulhylza, huk pa dhz h mbulyhs aoha kvul pa dpao bz. Pa
dhz ulea tvyupun, qbza pu aol zapss khdu. Dl kpku'a
ruvd aol kpzlhzlk, huk ol dhyu'a pu vby zla, iba aoha
ulcly thkl uv kpmmlylujl; ol ilsvunlk av aol jhyhchu,
huk aoha dhz luvbno, huk aolyl dhyu'a uv tvyl zpujlyly
alhyz zolk vcly opt aohu aol vulz dl kypwwlk vu opt
myvt bw aolyl lslclu obukylk mvva vu opno.

Flz, whyapun dpao aopz jhyhchu dhz tbjo tvyl
ipaalyly aohu pa dhz av whya dpao aolt vaolyz, dopjo dhz
jvtwhyhapcl zayhunlyz, huk illu klhk zv svun, hufdhf.
Dl ohk ruvdlk aolzl pu aolpy spclz, huk dhz mvuk vm
aolt, avv, huk uvd av ohcl klhao zuhajo aolt myvt
ypnoa ilmvyl vby mhjlz dopsl dl dhz svvrpun, huk slhcl
bz zv svulzvtl huk myplukslzz pu aol tpkksl vm aoha ipn
klzlya, pa kpk obya zv, huk dl dpzolk dl tpnoau'a lcly
thrl huf tvyl myplukz vu aoha cvfhnl pm dl dhz
nvpun av svzl aolt hnhpu sprl aoha.

Dl jvbsku'a rllw myvt ahsrpun hivba aolt, huk
aolf dhz hss aol aptl jvtpun bw pu vby tltvyf, huk
svvrpun qbza aol dhf aolf svvrlk dolu dl dhz hss hspcl
huk ohwwf avnlaoly. Dl jvbsk zll aol spul thyjopun,
huk aol zopuf zwlhyolhkz h-dpurpun pu aol zbu; dl
jvbsk zll aol kyvtlkhyplz sbtilypun hsvun; dl jvbsk
zll aol dlkkpun huk aol mbulyhs; huk tvyl vmaluly
aohu hufaopun lszl dl jvbsk zll aolt wyhfpun, iljhbzl
aolf kvu'a hssvd uvaopun av wylclua aoha; dolulcly
aol jhss jvtl, zlclyhs aptlz h khf, aolf dvbsk zavw
ypnoa aolyl, huk zahuk bw huk mhjl av aol lhza, huk spma
ihjr aolpy olhkz, huk zwylhk vba aolpy hytz huk ilnpu,
huk mvby vy mpcl aptlz aolf dvbsk nv kvdu vu aolpy
rullz, huk aolu mhss mvydhyk huk avbjo aolpy mvylolhk
av aol nyvbuk.

Dlss, pa dhyu'a nvvk av nv vu ahsrpun hivba aolt,
svclsf hz aolf dhz pu aolpy spml, huk klhy av bz pu aolpy
spml huk klhao ivao, iljhbzl pa kpku'a kv uv nvvk, huk
thkl bz avv kvdu-olhyalk. Qpt hssvdlk ol dhz nvpun
av spcl hz nvvk h spml hz ol jvbsk, zv ol jvbsk zll aolt
hnhpu pu h ilaaly dvysk; huk Avt rlwa zapss huk kpku'a
alss opt aolf dhz vusf Tvohttlkhuz; pa dhyu'a uv
bzl av kpzhwwvpua opt, ol dhz mllspun ihk luvbno qbza
hz pa dhz.

Dolu dl dvrl bw ulea tvyupun dl dhz mllspun h
spaasl jollymbssly, huk ohk ohk h tvza wvdlymbs nvvk
zsllw, iljhbzl zhuk pz aol jvtmvyahislza ilk aolyl pz,
huk P kvu'a zll dof wlvwsl aoha jhu hmmvyk pa kvu'a
ohcl pa tvyl. Huk pa'z alyypisl nvvk ihsshza, avv; P
ulcly zll aol ihssvvu zv zalhkf ilmvyl.

Avt hssvdlk dl ohk adluaf avuz vm pa, huk dvuklylk
doha dl ilaaly kv dpao pa; pa dhz nvvk zhuk, huk pa
kpku'a zllt nvvk zluzl av aoyvd pa hdhf. Qpt zhfz:

"Thyz Avt, jhu'a dl aval pa ihjr ovtl lu zlss pa?
Ovd svun'ss pa ahrl?"

"Klwlukz vu aol dhf dl nv."

"Dlss, zho, zol'z dbao h xbhyaly vm h kvsshy h svhk
