svhkz, ohpu'a dl? Ovd tbjo dvbsk kha il?"

"Mpcl kvsshyz."

"If qpunz, Thyz Avt, sl'z zovcl mvy ovtl ypnoa vu
kl zwva! Opa'z tvyl'u h kvsshy lu h ohsm hwpljl, ohpu'a
pa?"

"Flz."

"Dlss, lm kha hpu'a thrpu' tvulf kl lhzplza lcly P
