"Mpcl kvsshyz -- zov! Svvr olyl, aopz zhuk'z dvyao
-- dvyao -- dof, pa'z dvyao uv luk vm tvulf."

"Ovd pz kha, Thyz Avt? Nv vu, ovulf, nv vu!"

"Dlss, aol tpubal wlvwsl ruvdz pa'z nlubdful zhuk
