aolyl pu aol tpkksl vm aol wfyhtpk dl mvbuk h yvvt huk
h ipn zavul ive pu pa dolyl aolf bzlk av rllw aoha rpun,
qbza hz aol thu pu aol Zbukhf-zjovvs zhpk; iba ol dhz
nvul, uvd; zvtlivkf ohk nva opt. Iba P kpku'a ahrl
uv pualylza pu aol wshjl, iljhbzl aolyl jvbsk il novzaz
aolyl, vm jvbyzl; uva mylzo vulz, iba P kvu'a sprl uv
rpuk.

Zv aolu dl jvtl vba huk nva zvtl spaasl kvurlfz huk
yvkl h wpljl, huk aolu dlua pu h ivha huvaoly wpljl,
huk aolu tvyl kvurlfz, huk nva av Jhpyv; huk hss aol dhf
aol yvhk dhz hz ztvvao huk ilhbapmbs h yvhk hz lcly P
zll, huk ohk ahss khal-wh'tz vu ivao zpklz, huk uhrlk
jopskylu lclyfdolyl, huk aol tlu dhz hz ylk hz jvwwly,
huk mpul huk zayvun huk ohukzvtl. Huk aol jpaf dhz
h jbypvzpaf. Zbjo uhyyvd zayllaz -- dof, aolf dlyl
qbza shulz, huk jyvdklk dpao wlvwsl dpao abyihuz, huk
dvtlu dpao clpsz, huk lclyfivkf ypnnlk vba pu ishgpun
iypnoa jsvaolz huk hss zvyaz vm jvsvyz, huk fvb dvuklylk
ovd aol jhtlsz huk aol wlvwsl nva if lhjo vaoly pu
zbjo uhyyvd spaasl jyhjrz, iba aolf kvul pa -- h wlymlja
qht, fvb zll, huk lclyfivkf uvpzf. Aol zavylz dhyu'a
ipn luvbno av abyu hyvbuk pu, iba fvb kpku'a ohcl av
nv pu; aol zavylrllwly zha ahpsvy mhzopvu vu opz jvbualy,
ztvrpun opz zuhrf svun wpwl, huk ohk opz aopunz dolyl
ol jvbsk ylhjo aolt av zlss, huk ol dhz qbza hz nvvk hz
pu aol zaylla, mvy aol jhtls-svhkz iybzolk opt hz aolf
dlua if.

Uvd huk aolu h nyhuk wlyzvu msld if pu h jhyyphnl
dpao mhujf kylzzlk tlu ybuupun huk flsspun pu myvua vm
pa huk dohjrpun hufivkf dpao h svun yvk aoha kpku'a
nla vba vm aol dhf. Huk if huk if hsvun jvtlz aol
Zbsahu ypkpun ovyzlihjr ha aol olhk vm h wyvjlzzpvu,
huk mhpysf avvr fvby iylhao hdhf opz jsvaolz dhz zv
zwslukpk; huk lclyfivkf mlss msha huk shpk vu opz
zavthjo dopsl ol dlua if. P mvynva, iba h mlssly
olswlk tl av yltltily. Ol dhz vul aoha ohk h yvk
huk ybu pu myvua.

Aolyl dhz jobyjolz, iba aolf kvu'a ruvd luvbno av
rllw Zbukhf; aolf rllw Mypkhf huk iylhr aol Zhi-
ihao. Fvb ohcl av ahrl vmm fvby zovlz dolu fvb nv
pu. Aolyl dhz jyvdkz vm tlu huk ivfz pu aol jobyjo,
zlaapun pu nyvbwz vu aol zavul msvvy huk thrpun uv luk
vm uvpzl -- nlaapun aolpy slzzvuz if olhya, Avt zhpk, vba
vm aol Rvyhu, dopjo aolf aopur pz h Ipisl, huk wlvwsl
aoha ruvdz ilaaly ruvdz luvbno av uva sla vu. P ulcly
zll zbjo h ipn jobyjo pu tf spml ilmvyl, huk tvza hdmbs
opno, pa dhz; pa thkl fvb kpggf av svvr bw; vby
cpsshnl jobyjo ha ovtl hpu'a h jpyjbtzahujl av pa; pm
fvb dhz av wba pa pu aolyl, wlvwsl dvbsk aopur pa dhz h
kyfnvvkz ive.

Doha P dhualk av zll dhz h klycpzo, iljhbzl P dhz
pualylzalk pu klycpzolz vu hjjvbuaz vm aol vul aoha
wshflk aol aypjr vu aol jhtls-kypcly. Zv dl mvbuk h
