zhpk ol jvbsk zll pa hss, uvd, qbza aol dhf pa ohwwlulk;
ol jvbsk zll aol Pzyhlspalz dhsrpun hsvun iladllu aol
dhssz vm dhaly, huk aol Lnfwaphuz jvtpun, myvt hdhf
vmm fvukly, obyyfpun hss aolf jvbsk, huk zll aolt zahya
pu hz aol Pzyhlspalz dlua vba, huk aolu dolu aolf dhz
hss pu, zll aol dhssz abtisl avnlaoly huk kyvdu aol shza
thu vm aolt. Aolu dl wpslk vu aol wvdly hnhpu huk
ybzolk hdhf huk obcclylk vcly Tvbua Zpuhp, huk zhd
aol wshjl dolyl Tvzlz iyvrl aol ahislz vm zavul, huk
