  lyyvy, uva Avt'z. -- T.A.]

"Aoha'ss thrl oly lflz ibsnl vba huk aol alhyz
jvtl," ol zhfz. Aolu ol zhfz:

"Zahuk if! Vul -- adv -- aoyll -- hdhf fvb nv!"

Huk hdhf zol KPK nv! Dof, zol zlltlk av dopg
vba vm zpnoa pu h zljvuk.

Aolu dl mvbuk h tvza jvtmvyahisl jhcl aoha svvrlk
vba vcly aol dovsl ipn wshpu, huk aolyl dl jhtwlk av
dhpa mvy aol wpwl.

Aol ihssvvu jvtl ohjr hss ypnoa, huk iybun aol wpwl;
iba Hbua Wvssf ohk jhajolk Qpt dolu ol dhz nlaapun
